Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.98,0:01:05.62,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Hello, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.69,0:01:07.39,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Hello. Greetings. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:10.33,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Hi, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.39,0:01:12.66,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Hello! Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.70,0:01:16.45,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.45,0:01:19.40,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much. Thank you, thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.47,0:01:21.67,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,And welcome to The Grand Tour
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.74,0:01:24.94,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,which, once again, is in Whitby.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.14,0:01:31.50,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,There is actually a very good reason for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:35.12,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It is because these two last week blew up my house,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.12,0:01:37.42,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and I literally have nowhere else to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:38.62,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.69,0:01:41.19,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Plus... Plus, James May lost the tent bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.26,0:01:42.66,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Soz. - Yeah, he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.72,0:01:45.46,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,He did do that. Anyway, erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.53,0:01:48.86,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,we were reminiscing, as we've been here all week,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.93,0:01:52.53,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and we worked out that Yorkshire is the only place on earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.60,0:01:56.27,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,where all three of us have had a car crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.37,0:01:58.47,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,So what was yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.54,0:02:00.78,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,A Triumph 2500 rolled over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.84,0:02:03.11,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yeah. Hammond? - My first car.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:04.68,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,And my second car.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:07.68,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,My mum's car, my dad's car,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.75,0:02:09.38,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,my third and fourth cars,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:11.45,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,my first four motorcycles,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:13.25,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,the Radio York radio van,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.39,0:02:15.95,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,the Radio Leeds radio car,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.95,0:02:17.85,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and a jet-powered dragster.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.85,0:02:19.96,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:22.53,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,All of those. Busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:25.97,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,And, erm... And what about you in Yorkshire?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.97,0:02:28.50,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, me, I'll tell you. No, 1977,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.57,0:02:30.57,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,when the driving examiner said to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.64,0:02:32.94,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,"Congratulations, Mr Clarkson, you've passed,"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:35.91,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,what I heard was, "Congratulations, Mr Clarkson,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:38.45,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,you are the best driver I've ever seen."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:40.62,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Oh, no. - 36 hours later -
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:43.22,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That's all it was, 36 hours I'd been on the roads -
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:44.62,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,stuffed my mother's Audi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.69,0:02:46.45,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Wheels came off, killed a sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:50.42,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,So, if you're the farmer, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.43,0:02:53.10,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Er... Anyway, I'm glad we're still in Yorkshire,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:54.34,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,because last week
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:56.69,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,we said there was no real motoring connection
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:02:57.75,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,with the county
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:03:00.43,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and it turns out that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:02.81,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I was reading Trip Advisor last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:04.46,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, Trip Advisor is a website
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:06.18,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,for the mealy-mouthed and the bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:08.02,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, hang on. I mean, it's not entirely...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.03,0:03:10.92,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No, seriously, it's useless apart from anything else
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:13.34,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,because you have to know someone
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:15.61,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,before their opinion is relevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.27,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I mean, I know Hammond, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:19.69,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,So if he tells me a restaurant's great,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.71,0:03:21.55,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I know I don't want to go there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:23.21,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,because it'll be rubbish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:25.17,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You're absolutely right, actually
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:26.58,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,because that bloke in the hat over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:28.93,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't care how many stars he gives Oxfam Whitby
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:31.04,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm not going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:34.16,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Exactly. Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:36.68,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I went on Trip Advisor, OK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:38.85,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and there was a review of Whitby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:41.98,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,And it said, and I'm quoting here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:43.28,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,"One aspect of Whitby
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:46.05,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,," is the large number of local chavs..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:49.88,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,"...who drive around the town in a circuit
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:52.87,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,in their noise-enhanced cars."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:55.38,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Already, I don't like this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.55,0:03:57.65,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,"They accelerated down the narrow streets"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:04:00.14,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and then slowed their engines down quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:01.51,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,as they approached a junction,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:04.93,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,"causing explosive-sounding backfiring."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:07.65,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,He sounds like a right knob.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:08.71,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Of course he's a right knob,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:11.49,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,he's leaving a message on Trip Advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:13.21,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the police
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.26,0:04:15.28,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,the police, the local police here -
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:17.05,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,they've decided they've had enough of people
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:17.96,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,how they put it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:19.68,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,"...driving away in a manner
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:23.12,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,"that causes their wheels to spin and screech."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:24.79,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,OK? So they decided to have a clampdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:27.14,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,But, and this is the quote I love,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:31.12,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,"The operation was curtailed due to poor weather."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:34.17,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,What, are they saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:35.73,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,They didn't go out because it was raining?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:39.24,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No, law enforcement in Whitby is like cricket.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:41.72,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Everybody just goes inside if it starts to drizzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:43.73,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,So this is... This is the Whitby Town
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:44.81,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Police we are talking about here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:47.15,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, the WTPD. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.36,0:04:49.55,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No, hang on a minute
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:51.97,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,this is North Yorkshire. It's NYPD.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:55.38,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Wow! It actually is! It's the NYPD!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:57.40,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That would be a brilliant police drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:59.20,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,"Right, Constable,"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:03.06,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I've had the Chief Constable, he's chewed my arse,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:06.33,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,"the Mayor's chewed his arse, now we'll chew your arse."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.92,0:05:08.88,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,"We've got these lads - well, chavs -
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:10.87,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,"that are doing, like, wheel screeches,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:13.12,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and you've got 48 hours to solve it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:15.80,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,or I'll have your badge and your truncheon."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:20.41,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Anyway, on our car show tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:23.38,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,a tree falls over...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:27.15,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,...a hedgehog makes a noise...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:30.83,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,...and a dog eats some meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.17,0:05:34.28,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,But we begin with Porsche.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:38.25,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,They offer an immense complicated range of cars
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:41.46,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,all under the 911 banner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:43.67,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, Porsche enthusiasts
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:44.84,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,by which I mean these two imbeciles,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:47.26,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,say that they're all slightly different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:49.03,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:50.63,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No, slightly different,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:52.60,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and that the best of the bunch is something called
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:54.46,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,the GT3 RS.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.49,0:05:57.44,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,So I thought I'd take it to our track
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:05:59.05,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,to see what it was like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:01.74,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,And let's just hope that, for once in your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.76,0:06:03.94,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,you haven't behaved like a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:04.87,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.89,0:06:08.15,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Well, just said it's no good because I've got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.50,0:06:12.29,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Hammond, I am a professional motoring journalist
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:13.65,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and coming up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:17.05,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Amongst other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:20.77,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Coming up now is my professional review.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.81,0:06:27.30,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,This is the car in question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:30.76,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No, wait. Sorry. Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:33.25,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's easy to be confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:34.78,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:41.02,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,The hottest, hardest,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:44.24,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,tightest 911 of them all...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:47.31,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,...and the most exotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:07:01.69,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It has the fattest back tyres
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:03.32,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I've ever seen on a road car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:05.81,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It has scaffolding in the back for stiffness,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:08.52,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,carbon-fibre body panels for lightness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:11.12,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,The roof is made from magnesium,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:13.69,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,so if you turn it over and there are sparks,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.69,0:07:16.08,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,there will be a blinding flash of light,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.13,0:07:17.99,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and then you will have a convertible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:28.81,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Like many people
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:32.47,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't really like the idea of the Porsche 911
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:35.14,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and I certainly don't like the people who drive them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:37.91,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I find them flawed, in some dark
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.07,0:07:39.88,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and rather disgusting way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:41.72,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,But I will grudgingly admit
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:44.79,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,that even the basic cooking models are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:47.15,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,extremely lovely to drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.22,0:07:48.22,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:50.73,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,They're just very good sports cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.39,0:07:55.60,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,But what about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.73,0:07:57.16,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:07:59.59,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:08.61,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Straight away, I can tell you the engine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.66,0:08:10.92,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,is incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:14.59,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,There's no turbocharging.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.60,0:08:19.06,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's just a four litre flat-six, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:22.30,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,you get 500 horsepower.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.67,0:08:27.36,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,And its red line at 9,000rpm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:34.07,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,9,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:36.63,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That's bike territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:42.62,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,But the best thing is the way it goes round corners.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.11,0:08:46.17,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Because it's got four-wheel steering
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:50.45,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and because the engine is sitting right over the rear axle,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:53.85,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,the grip is just astonishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:01.44,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I've engaged all the hero buttons down here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:05.60,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,turned all the electronic driver aids off
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:09.17,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and let see if I can unstick it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:13.64,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,In here far too fast into Swindon Swings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:19.05,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Not "Swings," that's something completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.11,0:09:22.71,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,But, anyway, no loss of traction at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:29.19,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I thought, when I read the spec sheet on the RS,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:32.31,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,that Porsche had tried to make a supercar,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:33.98,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,a rival for Ferrari
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:36.46,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and McLaren and Lamborghini, but they haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.53,0:09:38.37,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's still a sports car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:41.31,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's still chuckable and deft.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:49.48,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Whoa! It's very, very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:50.85,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Annoyingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:10:00.25,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,But... is it as good as this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:03.37,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,the BMW M4 GTS?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.53,0:10:04.66,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Like the Porsche
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:08.18,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,it's made from exotic lightweight materials...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.11,0:10:12.68,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and fitted with scaffolding instead of back seats,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:14.77,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and enormous tyres.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:18.00,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:20.50,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,But there are some problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.86,0:10:25.10,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,When you arrive at a small speed hump in the Porsche
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:28.71,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,you raise its nose electrically and all is well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:33.57,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,But when you arrive at the same hump in the BMW...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:38.34,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,you will need a team of men to fold away the spoiler
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:40.53,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and adjust the ride height.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:42.90,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,This takes several hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:47.93,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,There are some other issues as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:53.54,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,To give owners the sense they're driving a racing car,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:56.15,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,all of the storage bins have been removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:10:59.13,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,There's no cubbyhole here, no door pockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:01.26,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That means there's nowhere to put anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:03.47,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,And I think that, on a day-to-day basis
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:05.99,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,that would drive you a bit mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.86,0:11:12.55,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Then there's the ride, which is extremely bumpy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.68,0:11:16.42,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and the drone from the tyres, which is horrendous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:21.08,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,After ten minutes on a motorway,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:22.48,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,you will have a headache
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:25.08,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and you won't have any headache pills with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:27.08,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,because there was nowhere to put them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:32.11,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, at this point, I would normally use the word "however"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:35.45,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and start talking about the car's good points.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.91,0:11:36.82,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:39.88,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I can't, because...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:43.90,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm struggling to find any.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:47.42,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,The engine, for example, has water injection,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:50.16,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,which sounds cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:53.44,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,But it means that every third time you fill the car with fuel,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:56.94,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,you have to fill a water tank in the boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:12:00.40,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but I'm not sure
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:03.64,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,this is very hi-tech.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:07.74,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,And then there's the steering
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:09.71,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,which in comfort mode is horrid
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:12.99,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and in sport setting is even more horrid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:16.15,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That said, the steering wheel is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:18.96,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's good and thick. It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:22.08,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:22.08,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's like holding onto something from the Ron Jeremy range.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:24.35,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,And the seats aren't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:25.80,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,But other than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:28.46,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:31.04,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,A point that becomes even more obvious
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.15,0:12:33.91,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,when you go into battle against the Porsche.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:42.37,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,We both have around 500 horsepower,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:45.57,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,both have a top speed of around 190,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:49.37,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,but the Porsche is a lot lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.17,0:12:53.00,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Probably because it doesn't have a tank
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.03,0:12:55.00,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,full of water in the boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:05.14,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Struggling to keep up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.56,0:13:09.58,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Here we go, into Swindon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:11.06,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, "Springs"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:12.92,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,A pampas grass shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:15.62,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh! We're having... God, that's nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:20.64,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,This is not a car that responds well
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:24.17,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,to my rather brutal driving style.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:26.96,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,The problem is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:31.63,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,it doesn't really respond very well to delicacy, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:38.93,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,This competition here now between these two cars
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:42.02,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,is like a boxing match between an actual boxer
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:45.76,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and someone who thinks they're a boxer
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.78,0:13:48.18,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,because they're wearing satin shorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:16.95,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,How did BMW get this thing so wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:18.85,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:23.92,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's twitchy, it's unpredictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:25.59,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,And in the rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:29.71,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,it's somewhere between spiteful and undrive...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:31.66,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, God! ...undriveable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:41.77,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,But, that said, this has to be the winner of this test
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.82,0:14:44.27,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,because Richard Hammond...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:46.84,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,...has got one of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:55.15,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I called it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:56.77,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That was annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:14:58.78,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That was a professional review.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:00.14,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,At points.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:02.20,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,But you were doing so well,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.27,0:15:03.73,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and then you ruined it at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:04.71,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, ruined it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.76,0:15:06.34,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,By saying you'd have a worse car
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:07.64,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,because I haven't got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:10.95,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- That Porsche wounded me. - Wounded you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:11.83,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It did wound me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:14.08,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,you know, it's got so much grip
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:15.53,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,that you're sort of forced into the seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.34,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,And the seat's got stitching on it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.38,0:15:19.01,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,which digs a hole in your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:20.98,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I've got a picture of what it did. Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.03,0:15:22.64,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That's my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:25.96,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm amazed you weren't hospitalised with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:26.76,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That's horrific!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:28.10,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- That is a savage wound!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:29.44,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,-Mine's never done that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.46,0:15:30.47,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That's cos you're a midget!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:32.21,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You don't reach that high up the seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:35.02,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Or maybe you're a freak and sit in the wrong place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.06,0:15:37.75,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's not just the fact it wounds you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:40.94,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Also, the Porsche's more expensive than the BMW.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.97,0:15:44.27,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, but I'd rather spend 131,000 on the Porsche
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:46.47,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,than 120,000 on a BMW
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.52,0:15:49.41,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,that's not very good on the road\Nnot very good on a track
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:51.41,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and no good at all in the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:52.75,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no, that's fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:54.05,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Hold on. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.09,0:15:56.32,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I've got to the bottom of the problem with the BMW.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:15:57.91,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's right here in the blurb.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:16:00.00,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,"Developed on the Nurburgring."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:03.66,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and, actually, speaking of tracks,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:06.79,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,it's now time to hand the M4 over
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:10.78,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,to a man who thinks that sparkling water is basically communist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:14.09,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, time to give it to the American.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.84,0:16:17.53,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.65,0:16:20.06,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,And he's off! No messing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:22.04,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Parps from the exhaust on the upshifts
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:24.58,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,as he attacks the Isn't Straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:26.58,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he actually knows what he's in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:28.09,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Driving a BMW.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:31.31,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,British Motor Works.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:33.73,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,So, that's a no, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.75,0:16:36.28,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,OK, continuing up the Isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:39.59,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,They say it's got more power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:43.36,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Than what, my damn toothbrush?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:45.48,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:48.40,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Right to the end of the Isn't now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.45,0:16:50.26,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and into Your Name Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:52.80,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Hard on the brakes, keeping it all in check,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.87,0:16:54.92,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and surely he'll appreciate the turbos
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.96,0:16:57.04,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,punching him out of the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:16:58.77,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Turbos on an engine is
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.82,0:17:02.11,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,God's way of telling you it ain't got enough cylinders.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:04.70,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,My mistake. Right, back up the Isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:06.62,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Really winding up that straight-six.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:09.81,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I must admit, from the outside, it sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:11.97,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,And already he's turning in hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:13.66,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,round the Unexploded Bomb,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:16.33,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,into the narrowness of Old Lady's House.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:20.56,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, back on the power for the bumpy bit towards Sub Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.61,0:17:23.62,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Idiotic splitter in peril over the ruts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:25.82,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Now working the ceramic brakes hard
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:27.12,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,for the tight left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:30.20,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Tickle of power. There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:32.49,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,And left again into Field Of Sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:36.34,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,A whiff of oversteer, and across the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:39.31,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It looked tidy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.34,0:17:40.80,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it looked all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:42.88,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It looked tidy. Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:45.28,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's bring up the er...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:46.88,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's bring up the leader board, if we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.91,0:17:48.19,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, there we are. We've already had
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:50.80,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,the 911 GT3 RS round.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:52.52,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Wha... And you're not gonna show the lap?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:54.07,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Nobody's interested in watching an American
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:17:57.13,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,being sawn in half by a glorified Beetle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:17:59.04,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It did 1:20.4.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:18:01.56,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Right, so, now let's see what the M4 did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:04.72,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's put the time up. There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.86,0:18:08.51,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Two seconds slower, and that's a short track.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:10.60,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That's unbelievable. That's not good, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:14.02,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No. It's only a second faster than a Porsche 718.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:16.66,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I know. I mean, I admire BMW
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.73,0:18:19.02,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,for trying with that car. I really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:21.17,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,But, my God, they've made a hash of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:23.33,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,In fact, I'm trying to think of a metaphor
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.55,0:18:27.27,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,for someone who's really tried their hardest with something
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:28.88,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and it hasn't worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:36.40,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No, nothing's coming to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:37.60,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I've got nothing. I've got nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:38.68,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I've got nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.69,0:18:40.89,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,So, let's... Let's move it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.96,0:18:44.86,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's time for us to make a gentle left into Conversation Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.53,0:18:55.49,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,OK. Right, I want to begin with the new Ford GT.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:57.86,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You've got a picture of it here. Now, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.89,0:19:00.44,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, you remember the last GT they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:03.66,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That was just an homage, really, to the old GT40.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.71,0:19:07.13,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,This one, they say, is actually a racing car on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.15,0:19:09.85,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's got a twin-turbo, 3.5 litre V6,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:11.31,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,seven-speed flappy-paddle box,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:12.89,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,more than 600 horsepower.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.95,0:19:17.23,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,The problem is, though, I can't think of any racing car
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.24,0:19:19.36,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,that works on the road, really, ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:20.13,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No, they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:23.67,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I mean, the Nissan GTR: fabulous, fabulous car.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:26.53,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Rubbish. It's undriveable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:27.93,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You know, it's a very good point,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.98,0:19:29.76,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,because a racing car on the road
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:32.48,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,is a bit like trying to play tennis with a cricket bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:33.73,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's technically possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:35.63,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Two totally different disciplines.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.66,0:19:39.26,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,The only trouble is, that looks so good, I do find myself going...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:43.37,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Mm. You erm... You bought the last GT, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:44.48,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:47.51,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you for reminding me, Hammond. Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:49.37,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Did that go well for you? - No, it didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.42,0:19:51.20,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, did it not? - No, it didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:52.68,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,The problem was the insurance company
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:54.15,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,said it had to have a burglar alarm,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:55.62,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,which blew usually
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:58.17,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,when my daughter was doing the school play and ruined it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.31,0:19:59.95,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and it had to have a tracker.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:03.08,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,And there is nothing on God's earth more annoying than a tracker.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:05.37,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,But I've got a tracker. It doesn't bother me in the slightest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:07.57,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No, that's because you'll have a little special place
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:09.56,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,on your hall table with a pencil outline.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:12.69,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,"I've got my keys and must remember to take my tracker."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.70,0:20:14.27,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Because you're organised and I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:15.94,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,One for your tracker, one for your keys
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:17.00,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,one for your little penknife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.03,0:20:18.97,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,One for some change in case you need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.04,0:20:20.67,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, with 10ps and 2ps.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.68,0:20:22.48,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,And a tiny screwdriver for mending your glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:23.95,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- He will. Oh, he will. - No, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.98,0:20:26.20,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No, it lives in a... It just has a little pouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:27.63,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You just hang it on the hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.65,0:20:28.92,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Oh, does it? - You've got a pouch?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:31.01,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,He's got a pouch for his tracker.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:32.65,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Especially for the tracker?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.72,0:20:34.69,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Well, yeah, because... - What's it made of?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:37.22,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Well, leather, I suppose. - A little leather pouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:38.81,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Did you make it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.87,0:20:40.46,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- No, it came... - A little leather pouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:42.28,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It came with the car, believe it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:44.91,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, so Ferrari sold it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:47.04,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Was it?600? I bet it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:48.54,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No, it just came with the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:50.17,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't think Ferrari give it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.24,0:20:51.91,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,The stripes on your Ferrari, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:53.37,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Two stripes, a bit like on that Ford.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:56.09,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,There are two stripes. How much did you pay for those stripes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:20:58.38,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, they were an option. They were 6,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.27,0:21:03.52,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Look. Listen, this is why I drive a Golf GTI, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.52,0:21:04.92,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Because you don't need an alarm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.97,0:21:05.87,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,you don't need a tracker
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:07.95,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and it's five insurance groups lower down
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:09.74,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,than the previous Golf GTI level.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:11.43,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Wow! - It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:13.76,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's because you can't crash it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:15.67,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I bet I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.43,0:21:18.79,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.83,0:21:20.14,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,have you two seen
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:22.55,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,have you two seen those new pedestrian traffic lights
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:23.76,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,in Trafalgar Square?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:26.37,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Which, if you're watching America\Nis in London, which is in Britain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.40,0:21:27.97,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Are these... Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.04,0:21:31.34,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,These are the ones that have got the two blokes on them, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.41,0:21:33.21,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,James, don't be sexist!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.28,0:21:35.55,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Why is that...? - No, because what if you're a lesbian?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.58,0:21:38.45,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, you would put two women on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:40.29,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, then what if you're straight?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.35,0:21:43.12,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- A man and a woman? - But traffic lights are only this big.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.14,0:21:45.29,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You can't have a man and a man, a man and a woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.31,0:21:47.79,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,a man who isn't sure, and a woman and a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.86,0:21:52.00,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,What if... What if you just want to cross the road?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.07,0:21:55.33,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,What... It's like being in the '70s with you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.40,0:21:58.25,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Crossing the road
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.28,0:22:00.42,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,is now an opportunity for you to express your sexuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:01.88,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It is. That's why
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:04.11,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,they've come up with these traffic lights in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.17,0:22:05.45,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,What are they for?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.49,0:22:07.55,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No, they really have. They really have.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.57,0:22:09.24,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- They're real? - They are for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.27,0:22:11.28,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,What's that one on the right, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.33,0:22:13.81,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Hello! Transgender.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.43,0:22:17.16,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,What? So, hang on, only tran...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.19,0:22:18.94,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yeah. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.97,0:22:20.73,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Transgender traffic lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.79,0:22:23.30,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- I didn't know that. - So only...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:26.20,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Only transgender people can cross when that's green?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.27,0:22:27.50,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.60,0:22:29.24,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,When it goes red, does that mean
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.30,0:22:31.17,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,it's not OK to be transgender?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.19,0:22:32.74,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That's a good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.77,0:22:34.40,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happens when it goes red.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.41,0:22:36.98,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No way they're gonna say, "It's not a..." I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:40.18,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,And what has any of this got to do with crossing the road?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.20,0:22:41.24,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That's all you want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.29,0:22:43.01,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's nothing to do with expressing your sexuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.04,0:22:45.12,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's the wrong time. I want to cross the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.17,0:22:45.98,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,All I want to do at that point
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:48.45,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,is work out how to go to the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.45,0:22:50.52,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.52,0:22:50.29,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,And by that I don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.08,0:22:53.33,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No. I don't..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.07,0:22:55.63,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.94,0:22:58.54,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,...of the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.65,0:23:00.38,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Maybe you're right, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.67,0:23:02.97,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Right, now, can I talk about Alfa Romeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.04,0:23:04.50,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- No. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.59,0:23:06.37,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Because we have to introduce our next film.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.44,0:23:09.14,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, as we know, in recent years the world's carmakers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.21,0:23:11.91,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,have made great strides to make more fuel-efficient
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.98,0:23:14.65,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and environmentally-friendly car engines,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.65,0:23:16.35,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,but very little has been done to make more
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.42,0:23:19.65,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,environmentally-friendly car bodies and interiors.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.69,0:23:23.02,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, by and large, they are still made of steel and plastic,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.09,0:23:25.22,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and that consumes a huge amount of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.29,0:23:26.45,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,So we had an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.49,0:23:30.24,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Are there more sustainable materials that could be used instead
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.30,0:23:33.83,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, to find out, each of us bought a Land Rover Discovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.90,0:23:36.07,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,We then removed its metal body
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:40.44,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and replaced it with whatever we thought was the best solution
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.51,0:23:42.71,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,for the future of the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.85,0:23:48.95,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,The meeting point was in Wales,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.02,0:23:51.38,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and I was the first to arrive,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.45,0:23:53.69,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,in a car made from mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.67,0:24:01.49,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,But, sadly, before I had the chance to tell you anything about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.56,0:24:02.86,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Hammond arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.27,0:24:13.76,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. Let me talk you through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.84,0:24:17.15,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,What I've done, I've built a frame out of hazel,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.18,0:24:19.98,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,through which I have weaved English flowers and shrubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.01,0:24:21.48,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's basically a hedgerow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.55,0:24:23.72,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Better still, it is growing, because I've planted them
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.72,0:24:27.05,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,so it's got compost and soil to provide the nutrients required
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.12,0:24:29.22,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,to let my car flourish and bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.29,0:24:31.02,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You don't... You don't wash this car
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.07,0:24:32.33,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,you water it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.41,0:24:34.76,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's alive. It's brilliant, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.83,0:24:37.36,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Clematis? - No, it's cleared up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.43,0:24:38.76,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Have you become a hippie?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.81,0:24:41.20,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No, but I can feel it starting inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.27,0:24:42.74,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- What have you done? - Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.80,0:24:44.80,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Sadly, before I could tell him,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.87,0:24:47.41,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Jeremy arrived... in a snuff movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.35,0:24:59.12,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, I can see what's happened. Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.19,0:25:03.96,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You're speechless, because all the words in your head
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.02,0:25:07.76,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,have been sucked out by the magnetism of my genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.79,0:25:11.23,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,A car made from bone and skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.30,0:25:13.84,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- What bones? - Animal bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.87,0:25:15.18,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Bones are no good for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.19,0:25:16.96,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You can't use bones to make cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.99,0:25:18.77,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Why not? When your dog dies
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.81,0:25:20.17,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,what do you do now? You bury it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.24,0:25:22.38,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- I don't turn her into a boot lid! - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.44,0:25:24.64,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Because I don't want to see a little face stretched across...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.72,0:25:27.40,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You don't have the face! I haven't got a face on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.48,0:25:29.40,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's just the bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.47,0:25:31.52,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,So as Granny gets older, does the family sit around
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.58,0:25:33.89,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,planning a new little hatchback?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.95,0:25:35.35,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, I hadn't thought of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.42,0:25:37.66,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,There's not a lot of dignity in it, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.79,0:25:39.43,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Have you used ears for wing mirrors?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.49,0:25:40.86,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yes. - You're sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.93,0:25:43.13,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Why would you not do that? They're designed for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.20,0:25:45.63,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- No, they're not. - Well, they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.70,0:25:46.79,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- They're not reflective.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.81,0:25:50.17,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- They absorb information and pass it on to the creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.24,0:25:51.94,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Look at my windscreen. - What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.01,0:25:54.07,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's... the digestive system -
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.14,0:25:56.81,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,well, part of the digestive system - of an cow.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.81,0:25:58.18,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,What part of the digestive system?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.24,0:26:00.31,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Its stomach lining. - Not its stomach lining.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.38,0:26:02.18,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Well, where? Further back? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.25,0:26:04.98,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Are you staring at the world through a cow's ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.42,0:26:09.26,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It is its anal passage.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.32,0:26:11.98,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,But it's stretched so thin
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.05,0:26:14.05,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,it's completely transparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.08,0:26:15.91,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Cow's arse, horse's arse. It's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.98,0:26:20.40,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on! It's a lot better than what you two have done, which is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.47,0:26:23.14,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- What's this made out of? - Have a guess. -Is it mud?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.20,0:26:24.84,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's mud. It's a mud car.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.87,0:26:26.60,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- You've got flat tyres. - No, they're not flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.61,0:26:29.49,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,They're pumped up as high as they will go without exploding.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.53,0:26:31.14,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- How much does it weigh? - Quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.21,0:26:32.58,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- How much? - Yeah, loads.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.65,0:26:34.31,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,How much does it weigh, James?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.38,0:26:35.95,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- What units would you like? - Tonnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.02,0:26:37.65,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.72,0:26:41.55,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Five tonnes? Well, that's just idiotic.\N- Well, mud is quite heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.62,0:26:42.95,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- This looks safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.99,0:26:45.01,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- It's sustainable, is that. That is growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.10,0:26:47.10,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,While we've been having that conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.15,0:26:48.77,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,this has extended a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.79,0:26:50.80,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- It just grows quietly. - Is it actually a living car?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.85,0:26:51.80,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Everything's planted.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.85,0:26:54.10,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I've put bulbs along here, ready for spring. Daffodils.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.17,0:26:56.87,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Not safe, though, is it? - Yes. Hazel, very strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.90,0:26:58.54,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's not as strong as bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.59,0:27:01.30,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Bone is three times stronger than steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.36,0:27:02.41,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.48,0:27:05.22,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh. Sorry, text.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.28,0:27:06.98,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Mr Wilman.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.05,0:27:08.93,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,"Having built your cars from nature
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.98,0:27:10.95,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,," you will now drive through it,"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.02,0:27:12.63,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,to the Myarth Hill,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.66,0:27:16.06,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,"where you will take part in a green motorsport event."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.12,0:27:18.89,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- What green motorsport event? - He doesn't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.93,0:27:23.10,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,A motorsport event that is presumably ecological in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.16,0:27:24.16,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.23,0:27:25.54,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Before setting off,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.59,0:27:28.80,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,we consulted a map to see where we were going.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.90,0:27:31.30,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Right, so that's the UK.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.37,0:27:34.17,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,We're here, and we've got to get to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.28,0:27:39.48,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Well... that doesn't look like too much of a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.73,0:27:42.85,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,With that sorted, we saddled up
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.89,0:27:46.52,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and began our epic 11-mile journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.82,0:27:49.30,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Look at the smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.34,0:27:50.69,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That's ecological.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.76,0:27:54.53,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Greenpeace are gonna be ringing him up at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.59,0:27:56.30,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Tremendous.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.36,0:27:58.97,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Smells of nature, I'm in nature,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.03,0:28:01.09,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm made of nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.50,0:28:02.95,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's not quick
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.98,0:28:06.37,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,but it gives me more time to enjoy God's creation,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.44,0:28:09.18,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,of which I am very much a part.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.24,0:28:11.21,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.54,0:28:14.55,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,James!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.52,0:28:22.99,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,We've done ten seconds, and James...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.06,0:28:24.56,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I may be losing one of my
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.59,0:28:26.89,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I think the correct technical term is the A-pillar.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.16,0:28:29.00,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Now it's gone completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.87,0:28:33.15,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.10,0:28:39.26,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Surely he has to admit defeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.64,0:28:41.77,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,There's not much car left now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.84,0:28:44.71,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear, James.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.78,0:28:46.28,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I think we can count you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.35,0:28:47.77,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- But it doesn't matter. - What doesn't matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.78,0:28:50.05,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Look. You think, "Oh, James's car's falling apart."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.12,0:28:54.15,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm standing in my spare-parts department. All of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.22,0:28:56.25,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Can be used to rebuild your car?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.28,0:28:57.20,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- It's right under there, mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.22,0:28:59.75,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,So it's as good as new? -Sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.80,0:29:03.66,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sorry, but we're gonna set off and leave you behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.70,0:29:05.05,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, hang on. You can't leave me behind
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.07,0:29:06.55,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,because we haven't started. We're still in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.57,0:29:07.90,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Oh, yes. - Good point. OK, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.95,0:29:10.64,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,we're gonna set off and go to the pub.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.70,0:29:12.57,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- That's a very good idea. - While you...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.64,0:29:15.47,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- While you... - ...find some mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.54,0:29:18.01,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I've lost my car! Oh, it's there. It's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.68,0:29:21.55,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,With Bob The Builder out of the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.61,0:29:23.75,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Richard and I settled down to appreciate
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.82,0:29:28.45,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,the planet-saving nature of our revolutionary eco-cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.92,0:29:31.72,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You may be...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.79,0:29:33.23,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,amused by my bodywork,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.29,0:29:35.46,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,or perhaps horrified,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.53,0:29:40.27,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,but the fact is that making steel bodies for cars
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.33,0:29:46.57,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,produces 120 million tonnes of carbon dioxide every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.64,0:29:49.04,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,120 million tonnes!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.08,0:29:53.08,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Carmakers will sort out clean,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.15,0:29:55.81,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,environmentally-friendly engines. They will.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.88,0:29:57.06,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,But in the meantime
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.10,0:30:00.29,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I can tell you that the CO2 produced by this car's engine
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.40,0:30:04.46,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,is being absorbed and used by the bodywork.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.66,0:30:08.76,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Plants breathe in carbon dioxide and breathe out oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.94,0:30:12.26,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That's what my car's body is doing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.53,0:30:17.60,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Jumpers, Sunday lunch... spare parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.03,0:30:21.08,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You don't need a foundry or a furnace
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.12,0:30:22.73,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,to build the body for this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.78,0:30:26.10,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You just need animals to make love to one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.26,0:30:30.24,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That's what this car is really. It's a sex machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.59,0:30:35.78,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, back at base, James was having a rethink.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.07,0:30:38.56,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I've decided to abandon my original idea
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.60,0:30:41.02,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,because it was just too weak and too floppy,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.05,0:30:44.21,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and instead I'm going to build a car out of bricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.24,0:30:46.11,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,The basic materials for making the bricks
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.14,0:30:49.37,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,are fresh mud with a bit of water in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.42,0:30:52.52,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,er... some straw to give it strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.54,0:30:54.62,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and some sheep poo.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.65,0:30:57.29,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You then use that to make the brick shape,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.33,0:30:59.11,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and then you fire those in a kiln.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.13,0:31:01.67,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Then you use the bricks to build the thing like a house.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.70,0:31:04.99,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Except, of course, it will be roughly the shape of a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.57,0:31:11.10,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Back on the road, Hammond had called our eco convoy to a halt.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.14,0:31:13.60,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- What's the matter? - Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.65,0:31:15.03,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Shush what?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.33,0:31:17.27,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,There's a bustle in my hedgerow.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.51,0:31:25.14,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.51,0:31:20.62,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, don't be alarmed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.88,0:31:25.14,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- It's probably just a... spring clean. - What, for the May Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.67,0:31:29.30,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,As it turned out, I'd picked up a passenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.00,0:31:32.16,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Hold on. There! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.18,0:31:34.49,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's a hedgehog!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.51,0:31:36.12,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah! He's moved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.41,0:31:40.11,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Do hedgehogs have bones? He could be a door mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.13,0:31:42.73,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,He's now a member of my little community in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.74,0:31:44.74,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You're not using him to make a door mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.79,0:31:46.48,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- No, but when he dies... - He lives here!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.58,0:31:48.65,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Hedgehogs die.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.81,0:32:12.58,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's got a mouse in his little bird box.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.61,0:32:16.15,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,And it's got the biggest testes I've ever seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.65,0:32:21.91,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Eventually, Richard and I arrived at the pub.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.31,0:32:27.90,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello! Oh, mate! You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.34,0:32:31.31,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh! Oh, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.34,0:32:33.36,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Clean break. That'll never... You're gonna need pins.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.40,0:32:36.54,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Your car's given me hay fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.57,0:32:37.96,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I can't see through my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.00,0:32:40.95,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you crashed your car because mine's got flowers on
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.98,0:32:42.79,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and not because you built your windscreen
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.81,0:32:44.25,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,out of a cow's balloon knot?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.29,0:32:46.75,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's not get bogged down with who caused the accident
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.78,0:32:47.67,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,cos it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.70,0:32:49.94,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I am now gonna go and get some spare parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.99,0:32:50.89,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Of course you are. That'll be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.90,0:32:53.10,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Maybe there'll be a nice zoo in this tiny village.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.14,0:32:54.72,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No, hospital. Old folks' home.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.75,0:32:57.20,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You could wait... Just find one of those old ladies with...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.19,0:33:00.65,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Back at the start point,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.70,0:33:03.75,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,the eco-warrior was ramping up the pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.50,0:33:25.08,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Watch that go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.88,0:33:28.69,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, back at the pub,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.73,0:33:31.65,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I was repairing my damaged front end.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.17,0:33:35.05,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, annoyingly, the pork that I bought
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.13,0:33:37.09,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,is sort of triangular and doesn't look right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.11,0:33:39.69,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It doesn't really fit, so I've got a side of beef,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.77,0:33:41.20,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,which I think will be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.23,0:33:43.96,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, I'm just erm... clearing away the old bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.85,0:33:54.77,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No, shoo! Shoo in Welsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.44,0:33:56.99,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm warning you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.44,0:34:00.28,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,How would you like to be a petrol filler cap?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.15,0:34:05.58,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.73,0:34:07.34,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I actually think it looks rather stylish,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.35,0:34:11.48,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,because it immediately looks ecological, recyclable,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.51,0:34:13.58,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,sustainable - all those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.58,0:34:16.38,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You get a single-skin brick wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.38,0:34:18.74,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It builds up very neatly, as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.81,0:34:21.68,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It is exactly the same as making something out of Lego.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.74,0:34:24.36,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,If you have lots of Lego...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.38,0:34:32.00,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.14,0:34:37.28,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Clearly, James was not going to get his car built that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.30,0:34:41.51,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,so Richard and I decided to spend the night at the pub.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.33,0:34:44.24,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,How far have we come today? Just remind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.30,0:34:46.22,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,We're still in the same field where we started.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.26,0:34:47.51,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Well, he is. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.56,0:34:50.87,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,We're in a pub. - But we have to go back to the start to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.33,0:34:54.45,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- It's not the best start. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.50,0:34:56.74,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Erm... - How do we know? We haven't started yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.75,0:34:59.15,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Precisely, so, actually, it might yet be a brilliant start
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.17,0:35:01.05,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,when the start starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.70,0:35:14.10,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,His one was useless
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.15,0:35:16.86,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's his slap-happy attitude to making things.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.88,0:35:18.47,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Attention to detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.54,0:35:19.38,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.41,0:35:23.96,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Anyway, now it is time for Celebrity Brain Crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.08,0:35:32.09,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, last week...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.49,0:35:34.14,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Last week, as I'm sure you'll remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.15,0:35:36.53,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,our guest Simon Pegg
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.56,0:35:39.12,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,sadly fell into the harbour and drowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.19,0:35:42.13,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Er... But there's no danger of that happening this week
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.19,0:35:45.62,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,because our guest is actually starting in the harbour.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.65,0:35:48.53,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,He is one of Britain's top comedians
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.56,0:35:50.97,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and a jet-ski enthusiast.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.01,0:35:55.24,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen, please welcome Jimmy Carr!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.71,0:35:58.95,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Here he comes now, look, on the screen...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.01,0:36:01.04,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and he's looking good!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.06,0:36:03.82,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,He is. What are we going to ask him when he gets here?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.88,0:36:06.37,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna ask him, actually, about erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.42,0:36:08.53,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,that story he told me once when we were on holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.56,0:36:10.45,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No, you can't ask him about that on air.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.49,0:36:12.16,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Ofcom, they won't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.22,0:36:13.84,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Why does Ofcom... We're on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.89,0:36:17.05,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but we're still broadcast. You can't tell that story.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.28,0:36:20.24,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Hang on! Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.30,0:36:22.74,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't want to interrupt. He's come in very hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.79,0:36:26.11,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No, what's this boat doing? Shush, everyone! Shush!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.18,0:36:27.74,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,The boat! Stop the...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.74,0:36:29.55,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, for God's sake! The boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.02,0:36:33.06,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.10,0:36:52.17,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,As you may have noticed,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.19,0:36:59.77,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,the audience there applauding the tragic death...\N...of one of Britain's best-loved comedians, Jimmy Carr.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.58,0:37:03.01,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Does that mean he's not coming on, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.11,0:37:05.78,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, James, he's burst
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.81,0:37:08.89,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and is now basically chum on the waters of the harbour,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.94,0:37:11.31,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,so that's a no, he's not coming on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.34,0:37:12.95,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,This is a dis... It's awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.01,0:37:13.90,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's every single week.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.92,0:37:15.89,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,We're getting a reputation. People are gonna notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.95,0:37:16.85,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's OK, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.87,0:37:21.49,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I've just thought of something else we can do to fill the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.57,0:37:22.86,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You... You know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.88,0:37:25.26,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- You go outside, and you. - Do I have to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.30,0:37:27.59,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm afraid you do. Could you go that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.62,0:37:29.54,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Go get it. Quickly, quickly. Run, run, run.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.60,0:37:31.00,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.06,0:37:33.15,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,please try not to look at the hideous
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.18,0:37:35.64,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,bloodstained water out of the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.37,0:37:38.37,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You see, the thing is... The thing is
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.39,0:37:41.65,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,that when immigrants try to get into the country,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.70,0:37:44.22,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,they always come in the back of a container lorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.28,0:37:45.47,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and I always think that is the world's
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.49,0:37:47.81,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,worst game of hide-and-seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.86,0:37:50.00,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Cos if you work for Homeland Security...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.01,0:37:50.89,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,... No, what's it called here?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.96,0:37:52.62,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Border Force?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.65,0:37:54.96,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,you open the doors and, "Well, there you are."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.03,0:37:56.86,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,So I was thinking surely
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.89,0:38:00.43,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,there must be a better way of getting into Britain?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.45,0:38:03.47,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,And I think I've worked it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.51,0:38:06.60,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,So, James, could you bring the car in? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.67,0:38:07.63,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.69,0:38:09.21,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Right, here he comes now,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.27,0:38:11.98,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,at his usual top speed of eight,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.04,0:38:15.70,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,in what is an Audi TT Quattro.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.72,0:38:17.12,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That's perfect. Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.14,0:38:18.57,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,. If you'd like to step out.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.61,0:38:23.03,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, Richard Hammond is in this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.49,0:38:27.40,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to give you, the studio audience
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.42,0:38:28.79,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,one hour to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.81,0:38:30.31,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, not an hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.43,0:38:31.91,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,All right, not an hour. A minute
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.93,0:38:34.09,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll give you 60 seconds to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.12,0:38:36.60,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Help yourselves, everybody. See if you can find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.67,0:38:38.36,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Open the bonnet. - Look in the ashtray!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.80,0:38:42.14,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Look in the ashtray? He's small, but he's not that small.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.21,0:38:44.01,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Open the boot. - Inside the seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.55,0:38:46.21,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,"Inside the seat."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.28,0:38:48.15,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,He's strapped underneath. He's underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.21,0:38:50.26,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Have a look. - I'll get down.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.32,0:38:52.40,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,If you just go down there, you can have a look underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.45,0:38:53.71,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Has anyone lifted this?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.86,0:38:56.36,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Three, two, one...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.39,0:38:57.99,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No, you've all failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.06,0:39:00.29,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You'd be no good in Immigration.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.28,0:39:04.85,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Right, go back to where you were, because, ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.89,0:39:07.87,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,what we are going to do now is reveal to you
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.91,0:39:11.58,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,where Richard Hammond was concealed in this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.61,0:39:13.44,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,James, could you give me a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.51,0:39:15.88,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Certainly. - Okey-doke.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.96,0:39:17.58,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Hello! - There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.61,0:39:21.83,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Hello! I'm in the car. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.33,0:39:25.85,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.93,0:39:28.29,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Can I get out now?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.35,0:39:31.72,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,The amazing thing is, it's not just Audi TTs.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.79,0:39:34.37,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Almost any car has that much space
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.41,0:39:36.53,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,if you want to do a spot of people smuggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.59,0:39:39.40,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's not that much space, just to be clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.46,0:39:40.74,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Can I get out now?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.80,0:39:43.74,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No, because I've just thought of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.83,0:39:45.79,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No, seriously. James, could you pop the bumper back on?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.82,0:39:47.54,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- What? - No, move your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.61,0:39:49.95,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- No, because... - It's not very nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.01,0:39:53.25,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Is it not? Right, so, pop that back on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.31,0:39:55.26,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, what we've got here, I think,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.31,0:39:59.14,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,is a really rather effective parking sensor.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.20,0:40:02.80,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,What? I don't like this! I like it. I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.83,0:40:06.12,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You get back in. We'll bring a car in so that...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.19,0:40:07.99,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so you've got something to reverse up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.03,0:40:10.20,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I need to drill some holes for your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.24,0:40:12.17,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You bloody don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.73,0:40:14.73,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Seriously, Hammond
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.74,0:40:17.10,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,you won't be able to see anything unless I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.10,0:40:18.47,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Where are your eyes? About here?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.49,0:40:19.73,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,At the front of my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.75,0:40:21.96,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Right, close them, Hammond. This...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.38,0:40:33.61,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Hammond? - I'm not talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.07,0:40:37.39,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Right, I'll do one for your other eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.14,0:40:42.87,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,There. Can you see out now?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.26,0:40:45.30,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, there. Look. Can you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.36,0:40:47.03,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,We can see his little eyes. That's lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.04,0:40:48.44,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,If someone holds this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.49,0:40:51.30,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Right, James, if you'd like to start reversing,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.37,0:40:54.77,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,keeping your ears open for Hammond's pitiable screams.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.84,0:40:55.98,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.04,0:40:58.46,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No... No! No! Just stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.50,0:41:00.36,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.41,0:41:03.27,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- How far away is that? - About 15 feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.15,0:41:05.54,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- What? - Hammond?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.56,0:41:07.30,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- What? - We live in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.35,0:41:10.30,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You could build a 4 million house in that gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.52,0:41:12.51,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I need to know when you're half an inch away.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.56,0:41:15.41,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You're not the one in the bloody bumper!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.48,0:41:17.63,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Right, come on, then, James. - Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.70,0:41:20.03,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Hammond, you're on silence till it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.30,0:41:28.10,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.97,0:41:32.04,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That is absolutely brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.83,0:41:35.11,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That's like a quarter of an inch.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.62,0:41:37.69,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.06,0:41:39.75,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Cor!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.89,0:41:44.15,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,The thing is, parking sensors are very expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.20,0:41:46.20,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You can rent a man for almost nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.25,0:41:49.54,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, look, I don't know how much you pay to rent a man normally,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.59,0:41:51.26,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,but I cost more.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.32,0:41:53.40,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, get me out of here, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.41,0:41:56.67,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, no, because we've got to link into the next film.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.19,0:41:58.95,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,We can't get you out anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.97,0:41:59.68,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,because you're too close
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.70,0:42:00.77,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,we'll never get the bumper off.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.77,0:42:03.71,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You're too good at your job, Hammond. Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.73,0:42:05.88,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That's what's happened. So we're going back...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.94,0:42:08.46,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's part two, isn't it? What was the film?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.79,0:42:11.45,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It was Italy. No, that was last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.86,0:42:14.92,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Oh, the cars! - Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.94,0:42:16.11,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Oh, the sustainable thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.13,0:42:18.91,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Sustainable cars. So... -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.93,0:42:24.33,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Get on with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.21,0:42:29.74,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,The following morning we were up bright and early
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.76,0:42:32.66,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,so we could get back to the start line.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.61,0:42:37.97,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Not a bad night, actually. - It was all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.01,0:42:39.64,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.94,0:42:42.74,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,May?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.31,0:42:48.49,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh! That's dogs and foxes and things, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.55,0:42:50.99,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Dogs have come and eaten your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.03,0:42:53.29,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,They haven't eaten it, they've destroyed it,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.36,0:42:56.52,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,which means I've got to put it back together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.73,0:42:59.75,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,There are some spare parts up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.42,0:43:02.67,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think that horse is looking very ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.69,0:43:04.37,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's got a very grey face.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.44,0:43:06.14,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That's always a sign of looking ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.20,0:43:08.31,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Is your horse ill?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.37,0:43:09.82,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- No. - No?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.89,0:43:11.31,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- No - He'll last the day, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.35,0:43:12.81,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.31,0:43:16.10,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.29,0:43:21.14,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It took all morning to repair my car
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.19,0:43:22.92,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,with stuff from the butcher's shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.99,0:43:24.92,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,which meant it was lunchtime
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.99,0:43:26.17,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,before we were on our way back
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.22,0:43:29.05,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,to see how James was getting on.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.89,0:43:33.95,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Jeremy, what's all that smoke up ahead there?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.15,0:43:35.61,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,What smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.70,0:43:38.98,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That massive ball of smoke in front of us, up front.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.01,0:43:41.64,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I can't see it. My hay fever's really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.66,0:43:43.35,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No, you can't see it because you're trying to looking at it
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.39,0:43:45.54,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,through a cow's butt hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.49,0:43:49.25,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,As it turned out, the smoke was on account
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.31,0:43:55.01,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,of James having single-handedly restarted the Industrial Revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.59,0:44:03.07,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.10,0:44:04.90,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- What are you doing? - I'm making...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.65,0:44:13.57,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,The theory is... we are reducing our impact on the environment,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.64,0:44:15.07,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,but you've dug it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.11,0:44:16.10,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's not where anybody lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.13,0:44:18.24,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's just the countryside. It's not doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.24,0:44:19.71,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Is that a coal lorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.78,0:44:23.23,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes. - The least environmental thing on the entire earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.28,0:44:26.22,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's a lorry delivering coal.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.28,0:44:28.52,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- So? - Why do you need coal?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.59,0:44:30.71,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- To fire up the kiln. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.76,0:44:32.86,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,The bricks have to be baked. You can't just...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.92,0:44:36.93,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Hold on. So you're making a car out of mud bricks? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.99,0:44:38.62,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna dig a canal network
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.65,0:44:40.31,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,to get in and out, perhaps, with your coal?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.38,0:44:42.87,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- That's quite a good idea. - It isn't a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.12,0:44:46.77,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Much ruined countryside later,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.84,0:44:50.48,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,James's new car was finally ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.54,0:44:53.20,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Why are you dressed up like an American footballer?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.26,0:44:55.15,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a prototype,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.22,0:44:57.38,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and I'm a test pilot, in effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.39,0:44:59.58,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Test pilots wear specialist equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.63,0:45:02.56,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,But that looks perfectly solid to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.81,0:45:04.99,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That roof is...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.24,0:45:08.16,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,James, even given the limitations of the material you've used,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.21,0:45:09.54,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,your car looks crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.59,0:45:11.63,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,But look how it blends in with the environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.63,0:45:13.11,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Prince Charles would love this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.15,0:45:14.31,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It doesn't blend in with anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.33,0:45:17.01,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,There's no environment left - you've dug it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.12,0:45:19.80,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Right, can we finally go? - Yes, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.84,0:45:22.07,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,11 miles lie ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.71,0:45:24.29,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,See you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.03,0:45:28.78,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.31,0:45:37.53,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That is a complete mystery, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.61,0:45:39.22,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.28,0:45:41.96,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It had an arched roof, it had a keystone.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.03,0:45:44.45,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,There must be something wrong with that mortar.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.64,0:45:47.75,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Waiting for James to mend his bodywork, again,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.82,0:45:50.99,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,meant my bodywork started to go off.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.39,0:45:56.15,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,But, eventually, he was ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.94,0:46:03.17,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's really rather pleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.42,0:46:06.07,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,This is like being at home with the windows open.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.49,0:46:10.59,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Richard, meanwhile, had added some floral go-faster stripes,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.66,0:46:12.94,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and I'd opened up my cow's rectum
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.97,0:46:15.13,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,to improve the ventilation.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.38,0:46:19.44,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,We have had a few problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.51,0:46:23.16,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,We've only covered, yes, two miles in two days,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.21,0:46:25.27,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,but here we are,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.31,0:46:28.34,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,as a threesome, going along.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.91,0:46:35.48,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.51,0:46:38.07,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's a river, and not a small one.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.13,0:46:45.09,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear. Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.80,0:46:50.35,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.83,0:46:52.62,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Oh, your bricks have fallen off, mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.65,0:46:54.07,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Your bonnet's fallen off.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.13,0:46:56.70,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Perfectly all right. Redundancy's built into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.74,0:46:58.63,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Is it? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.96,0:47:01.33,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Since Richard is the team bumpkin,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.37,0:47:04.08,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,we decided he should go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.74,0:47:07.85,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,OK, well, my community of people
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.88,0:47:09.03,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,make for higher ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.04,0:47:10.82,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Just climb.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.06,0:47:14.50,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Hammond's ark made it to the other side safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.55,0:47:16.30,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.46,0:47:18.75,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,And then it was my go.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.34,0:47:21.51,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm really deep here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.54,0:47:23.12,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Really, really deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.18,0:47:25.70,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Cows leak!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.76,0:47:28.51,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That's a terrible thing to learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.09,0:47:32.43,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,However, I, too, made it with relative ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.47,0:47:34.84,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Eat my meat, Hammond!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.08,0:47:36.93,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.03,0:47:38.84,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.90,0:47:40.16,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.20,0:47:43.80,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,An old man driving a low garden wall into a river.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.97,0:47:45.39,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's look on the bright side
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.41,0:47:47.22,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,If this doesn't work as a car,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.26,0:47:49.72,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,it will be very effective as a dam.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.35,0:47:55.96,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,He's not doing it quite as quickly as you or I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.03,0:47:58.36,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Nor as aggressively, nor as purposefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.54,0:48:01.52,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,His car is also riding a lot lower than ours
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.55,0:48:02.90,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,because it weighs so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.97,0:48:06.20,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I was getting very deep. It may be leaking slightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.17,0:48:09.99,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's leaking a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.07,0:48:14.69,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Cack. Chaps, I think I'm beached.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.73,0:48:17.34,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm being honest, there's not a great deal we can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.36,0:48:19.40,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You're in the river, we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.58,0:48:21.78,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Right, if I go right a bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.83,0:48:24.73,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I should... clear that...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.76,0:48:26.89,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.05,0:48:29.78,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, the... - The side's just come off. -Yeah, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.83,0:48:31.18,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,So the mortar's dissolving
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.21,0:48:32.60,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and the bricks are just falling off.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.64,0:48:33.98,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.14,0:48:37.68,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That's more gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.74,0:48:40.54,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, God! The mortar's dissolving!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.57,0:48:43.17,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,He's just transporting his own cameras along.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.24,0:48:44.51,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That's all he's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.55,0:48:45.91,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.14,0:48:49.65,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.71,0:48:52.19,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Little spindly arms throwing a brick.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.90,0:48:55.69,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.53,0:48:59.86,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,We're gonna have to put him out of his misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.88,0:49:02.85,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,We'll just abandon him. Do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.88,0:49:05.20,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,What is the point of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.26,0:49:06.86,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,James, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.93,0:49:09.97,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,We've analysed the situation and there is literally
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.03,0:49:12.10,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,nothing we can do to help. Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.43,0:49:15.96,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Leaving James in his dissolving car,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.02,0:49:20.63,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,we headed off to make camp and get supper underway.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.06,0:49:24.13,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, apart from your rather tragic tents,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.16,0:49:26.81,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- this isn't so bad. - It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.21,0:49:29.25,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It is amazing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.32,0:49:32.33,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,My car, the way it disappears into that hedge,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.37,0:49:35.54,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,it's not just camouflage, it is hedge.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.56,0:49:37.29,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- It's gone. - No, it is genuinely...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.35,0:49:41.45,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Actually, I will agree, yours is remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.57,0:49:46.07,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, James's car had shed so much weight
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.14,0:49:48.28,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,that he was able to get free...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.62,0:49:53.40,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and start raping the countryside again to rebuild it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.44,0:49:54.91,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.80,0:50:00.48,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You know, what's incredible about this -
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.62,0:50:03.50,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,this sustainable living we're doing
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.26,0:50:07.92,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,is our barbecue is made from bricks from James's car,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.53,0:50:11.14,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,the kindling and the vegetables are from your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.89,0:50:14.62,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Are you about to tell me I'm eating...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.33,0:50:16.60,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Back wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.09,0:50:23.78,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,What? - When you buy a steak, it says "keep refrigerated".
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.84,0:50:25.55,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It doesn't say, "Stick to the side of your car",
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.62,0:50:28.01,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,leave in the sun, then drive through a river."
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.58,0:50:49.26,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,James is making such a racket, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.66,0:50:51.75,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's worse than last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.40,0:50:56.20,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,The difference on this trip, while he's been tearing nature apart,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.23,0:50:59.18,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I've never felt closer to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.24,0:51:01.60,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, he's just messing everything up. He always...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.40,0:51:09.15,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Holy cow.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.26,0:51:10.89,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Hammond. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.63,0:51:14.43,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.44,0:51:18.00,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.06,0:51:19.64,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,He couldn't see it. It's a hedge trimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.68,0:51:22.92,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That's my community, you rural bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.96,0:51:26.47,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Oh, my... - Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.15,0:51:30.31,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,The next morning, to cheer up Hammond
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.35,0:51:32.45,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,following the decimation of his car
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.49,0:51:35.18,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and his woodland animal community,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.19,0:51:37.20,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I made breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.06,0:51:40.31,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Eat it. - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.34,0:51:42.31,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Why not? - Because it's going green!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.34,0:51:43.96,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's just a bit of door.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.02,0:51:45.78,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,You can see where the flies have been on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.82,0:51:47.11,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.14,0:51:48.44,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Hello. Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.66,0:51:49.55,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.90,0:51:53.43,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- It's a dung heap. - It is a dung heap.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.07,0:51:58.42,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Morning. - Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.44,0:52:00.03,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Is this a car? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.05,0:52:04.23,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It is a totally sustainable car made of,\Neffectively, wattle and daub,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.27,0:52:06.20,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,only the wattle has been replaced by straw
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.23,0:52:08.38,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and the daub has been replaced by cow poo,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.49,0:52:09.84,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,but the principle is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.99,0:52:12.58,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,How the hell do you fit in it? Only just.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.69,0:52:14.59,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Where's your windscreen? - There.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.86,0:52:15.75,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.20,0:52:19.62,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Can we just test your blind spots, James?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.93,0:52:22.49,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Can you see either of us now?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.00,0:52:24.11,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.71,0:52:28.33,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Heavily pedestrianised areas should be avoided.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.22,0:52:33.91,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Right, come on. We've just got two miles to go. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.38,0:52:36.20,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.21,0:52:37.81,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,The smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.87,0:52:41.11,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,What's that? - It breaks my heart, but it's a small gift for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.33,0:52:45.62,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Is it? Mate! - Yes, from me and my woodland community.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.66,0:52:46.93,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.93,0:52:49.72,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- It's a dead bat! - Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.81,0:52:52.15,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Bats have sonar, don't they? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.40,0:52:55.09,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,So I could use it as a reversing parking sensor.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.39,0:52:58.13,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't think it works once the bat is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.51,0:53:03.23,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,And so, with all of us running...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.95,0:53:09.74,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,My reversing bat is working well.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.81,0:53:14.18,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,...we began the final two-mile leg of our epic journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.82,0:53:16.33,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.95,0:53:20.49,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,There are some issues associated with environmentalism,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.56,0:53:22.84,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and we're seeing one of them right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.89,0:53:32.96,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Am I anywhere near the gate? - Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.59,0:53:40.35,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,James attempted to tie his car back together using a ball of string...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.43,0:53:42.44,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,which went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.53,0:53:44.98,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's going...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.71,0:53:50.60,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's gonna confuse him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.75,0:53:54.19,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Why'd they make it in a ball shape? What a stupid idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.66,0:53:59.02,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,But eventually it was done and we were on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.91,0:54:04.24,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,James, how much does it weigh now?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.26,0:54:06.27,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna say the weight has gone down a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.29,0:54:07.93,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I think I'm down to three tonnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.16,0:54:10.70,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,So you still need an HGV licence?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.77,0:54:13.62,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,But it's not a type of car known to the DVLA.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.88,0:54:18.73,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Mind you, I had even bigger problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.78,0:54:21.98,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,My car was starting to smell really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.31,0:54:25.11,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,One of the sound recordists
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.15,0:54:26.86,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,just came to fiddle with my microphone,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.90,0:54:28.72,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and actually was sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.73,0:54:33.84,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Eventually, though, our destination hoved into view.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.95,0:54:39.23,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,After three days gruelling travel
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.30,0:54:42.04,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,over 11 miles, we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.95,0:54:44.42,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,This must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.02,0:54:49.42,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.45,0:54:52.91,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,on a track carved out of nature itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.64,0:54:56.45,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.72,0:54:59.34,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- A text message. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.38,0:55:00.88,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I've got a text here from Mr Wilman,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.91,0:55:02.76,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,with the instructions of what we're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.78,0:55:07.06,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,"Whoever does the most laps in one hour wins."
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.20,0:55:08.88,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, James, that's not gonna be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.92,0:55:11.89,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Well, you don't know. - No, I do know it's not gonna be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.92,0:55:14.60,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, wait. Hang on. "You will be racing against
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.67,0:55:17.44,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,three old-fashioned steel cars."
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.91,0:55:20.02,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Hang on. Yes, those. - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.28,0:55:23.80,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Oh, there they are. - How quaint.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.87,0:55:26.24,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No, they don't look quaint. They look ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.33,0:55:28.08,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's funny, that's the nature of progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.11,0:55:30.62,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- Suddenly, they look stupid. - They do.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.22,0:55:36.71,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,The museum pieces were being driven by three local yobbos.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.93,0:55:39.24,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Right, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.73,0:55:44.16,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,The MeaTI, the TreeTI and the PeaTI are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.77,0:55:52.50,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, what a start! It's a good start.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.53,0:55:54.79,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, we're blocking!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.82,0:55:58.74,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, they've gone! They've gone! I couldn't see the flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.20,0:56:02.78,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, there are some hay bales. I'll follow those.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.51,0:56:05.40,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Where the hell does it go next?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.22,0:56:09.62,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Despite the excellent start from Richard and I,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.69,0:56:13.01,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,we were quickly overwhelmed by the steel cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.12,0:56:15.44,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,And now the Golf's got past!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.31,0:56:19.41,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.45,0:56:22.14,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I've let the Mondeo through. That's a disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.71,0:56:26.40,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've lost one of my nose tampons!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.47,0:56:29.84,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,What Richard and I really needed was help from our colleague.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.22,0:56:31.75,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Sadly, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.64,0:56:36.41,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna take a racing line. Oh, I'm completely lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.42,0:56:39.93,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,The trouble is, the race track looks the same as the front of the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.11,0:56:42.52,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,What a stupid idea for an event.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.33,0:56:47.79,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I've lost the other nose tampon! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.38,0:56:51.30,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I may have to pit for another tampon.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.71,0:56:53.98,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Where am I going?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.84,0:56:57.18,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,All right, James?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.26,0:56:58.46,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.69,0:56:59.93,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,No time to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.80,0:57:05.29,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I've gone for the super absorbent,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.51,0:57:07.55,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,slightly larger nose tampons,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.32,0:57:10.28,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,which I hope will last a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.31,0:57:17.06,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Given that we were in an endurance race,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.15,0:57:20.69,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,our tactics so far had been to protect our cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.11,0:57:25.18,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Reliability, that's what we need here. That is everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.31,0:57:26.84,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That's what matters most.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.98,0:57:30.40,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,But with the cars of the past racking up so many laps,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.60,0:57:32.84,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,we had to get the hammer down.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.53,0:57:36.82,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,The MeaTI against the...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.89,0:57:40.73,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,whatever that is - 1.6 litre Golf.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.91,0:57:42.15,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.55,0:57:44.75,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes! I've got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.58,0:57:48.42,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Power sliding a hedge.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.60,0:57:50.00,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.09,0:57:57.23,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes. Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.84,0:58:02.00,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I think I've done a lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.26,0:58:08.24,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,With us three - well, two - making good progress,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.31,0:58:11.49,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,the cars from the past started to play dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.75,0:58:16.58,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That is out of order! They are getting violent!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.32,0:58:21.52,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh! Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.59,0:58:23.29,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I've lost a tampon again!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.89,0:58:26.86,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.04,0:58:28.63,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Think you can mess with us
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.70,0:58:30.40,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,just because we like trees, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.46,0:58:33.47,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That's out of order, mate. You can't. Have that!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.74,0:58:42.41,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,The bone is taking on the steel!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.40,0:58:46.44,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Although we were holding our own,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.47,0:58:50.69,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,the relentless pressure started to take its toll on our vehicles.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.64,0:58:56.63,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I've lost part of the hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.38,0:59:00.90,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,I can smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.06,0:59:03.63,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,What can I smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.42,0:59:06.69,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Is that from the exhaust?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.02,0:59:11.44,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,With Hammond distracted by the hot exhaust burning his bodywork,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.51,0:59:13.97,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,it was all down to my cow car.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.71,0:59:21.73,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Good dicing here between the past and the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.20,0:59:23.93,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,It's neck and neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.73,0:59:27.22,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.46,0:59:29.32,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.89,0:59:31.29,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.30,0:59:32.58,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, hell. I think it looks like
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.59,0:59:34.66,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Jeremy's got trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.04,0:59:38.09,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,How do you peel a cow?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.44,0:59:42.40,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Having eventually got to the overheating engine
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.46,0:59:46.06,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and seen it had become a production line for maggots...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.26,0:59:49.51,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,...I decided to go off and be sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.36,0:59:57.85,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Er... News from the Inaugural Sustainable Motorsport Event
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.91,0:59:59.84,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,On A Sustainable Track, or whatever it's called,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.04,1:00:03.72,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Jeremy Clarkson has retired with a maggot infestation.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.38,1:00:08.53,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,This meant all our hopes rested with Richard Hammond
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.64,1:00:10.63,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and his smouldering ark.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.84,1:00:14.89,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you ran wide!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.09,1:00:16.62,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.80,1:00:18.57,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.60,1:00:20.84,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.97,1:00:24.34,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! More news
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.39,1:00:27.66,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,from the Sustainable Motorsport Challenge is that... Ow!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.88,1:00:30.51,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,...Richard Hammond, I believe, is on fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.58,1:00:32.72,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,The garden centre is ablaze.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.58,1:00:36.82,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, God! Oh, no! Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.35,1:00:40.49,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,That's gonna make it worse!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.38,1:00:44.70,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,With Hammond's car on fire...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.62,1:00:50.13,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,mine alive, and James's disintegrating again...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.20,1:00:51.58,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.71,1:00:55.94,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,...we decided that environmentalism simply doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.84,1:00:59.38,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,And with that, back to...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.53,1:01:01.98,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,And with that, back to the tent.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.13,1:01:05.88,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Holy crap!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.64,1:01:14.89,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,- No, it didn't work. - No. So, there we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.46,1:01:18.73,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,There we are, we've looked into it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.75,1:01:20.20,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,We've looked into it thoroughly,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.33,1:01:23.77,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,and I'm afraid we're all doomed, we're all gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.83,1:01:27.00,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,And on that terrible disappointment, I'm afraid it's time to end.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.18,1:01:28.94,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,See you next week. Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.98,0:01:05.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.69,0:01:07.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,大家好 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:10.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.39,0:01:12.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,你好 大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.70,0:01:16.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.45,0:01:19.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.47,0:01:21.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到The Grand Tour
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.74,0:01:24.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,这次我们又来到了惠特比
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.14,0:01:31.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,原因很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:35.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为这两人上周炸了我的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.12,0:01:37.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,我现在真没地方可去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:38.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.69,0:01:41.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,另外 詹姆斯•梅还弄丢了他的帐篷包
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.26,0:01:42.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,-是哦 -没错 是他干的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.72,0:01:45.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,他确实丢了 不管怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.53,0:01:48.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,这周 我们回忆发现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.93,0:01:52.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,约克郡是世上唯一的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.60,0:01:56.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们仨都撞过车的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.37,0:01:58.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,你那次撞了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.54,0:02:00.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,撞翻了凯旋2500摩托车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.84,0:02:03.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,-哈蒙德你呢？ -撞坏了我的第一辆车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:04.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,以及第二辆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:07.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,我妈的车 我爸的车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.75,0:02:09.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的第三 第四辆车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:11.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的前四辆摩托车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:13.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,约克台广播车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.39,0:02:15.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,利兹台广播车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.95,0:02:17.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,还有辆直线加速火箭车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.85,0:02:19.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:22.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,就这些 我很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:25.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,你呢 在约克郡撞啥了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.97,0:02:28.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,我告诉你 在1977年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.57,0:02:30.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,当驾校考官告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.64,0:02:32.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,祝贺你 克拉克森先生 你通过了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:35.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,我听到的却是 祝贺你 克拉克森先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:38.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,你是我见过最好的司机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:40.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,-哦不 -36小时后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:43.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,只有这么久 36小时 我在路上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:44.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,搞坏了我母亲的奥迪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.69,0:02:46.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,轮子掉下来 杀死了一只羊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:50.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果你是那个农场主 那抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.43,0:02:53.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,总之 很高兴我们还在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:54.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为上个星期
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:56.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们说到这里的汽车交通
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:02:57.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,很不发达
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:03:00.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,后来证明这是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:02.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,昨天晚上我在浏览猫途鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:04.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在使用猫途鹰的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:06.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,都是些刻薄尖酸的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:08.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,等等 也不是完全
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.03,0:03:10.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 说真的 它真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:13.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为你在认识某人之后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:15.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,才能知道他的观点是否值得参考
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,比如说 我认识哈蒙德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:19.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果他告诉我某家餐厅很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.71,0:03:21.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,打死我也不会去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:23.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,肯定会很垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:25.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,你说的太对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:26.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,比如那边戴帽子的小伙子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:28.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,不管他给惠特比乐施会多少星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:31.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,我都不会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:34.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,确实 不管怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:36.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,我在看猫途鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:38.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,有一则关于惠特比的评论
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:41.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,我引用一下 他说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:43.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,"惠特比给人的一个印象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:46.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,是数量惊人的当地小混混
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:49.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们开着巨吵的车
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:52.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,绕着这个小镇兜圈"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:55.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,我已经开始不喜欢这人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.55,0:03:57.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,"他们在狭窄的道路上加速
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:04:00.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后在快到路口的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:01.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,猛刹车
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:04.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,发出爆炸般的引擎回火声"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:07.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,他听上去就像个智障
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:08.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,他当然是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:11.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,他在猫途鹰上留言哎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:13.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,不管怎样 警察
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.26,0:04:15.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,当地警察
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:17.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们决定 他们受够了这些人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:17.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们这样描述
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:19.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,"以一种让轮胎滑行"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:23.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,"和尖叫的方式来驾驶"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:24.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以他们决定镇压
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:27.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是这句引用我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:31.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,"由于天气状况恶劣 行动取消"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:34.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以他们是说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:35.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,外面下雨啦 干脆别出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:39.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 惠特比警察就像蟋蟀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:41.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,毛毛雨就让人躲到屋里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:43.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,那么 我们说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:44.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,惠特比警察对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:47.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,-是的 所谓WTPD  -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.36,0:04:49.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,不对 别急
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:51.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,这里是北约克 应该是NYPD
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:55.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,-哇 还真是 -这可是NYPD
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:57.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,这会是部很棒的警察剧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:59.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,"好了 各位警官
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:03.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,警长对我很不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:06.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,市长对警长很不爽 因此你们的后果很严重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.92,0:05:08.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们这有些小姑娘 小混混 他们天天搞事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:10.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,比如让轮胎尖叫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:13.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,你有48小时来搞定他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:15.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,不然我就没收你的警徽和警棍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:20.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,总之 在我们今晚的汽车节目里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:23.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,一棵树倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:27.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,一只刺猬发出了声响
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:30.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,还有一只狗在吃肉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.17,0:05:34.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是我们要先谈谈保时捷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:38.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们的911系列中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:41.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,有着数量庞大的各式车型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:43.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,如今 保时捷脑残粉们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:44.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,也就是这俩蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:47.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,说这些车型都有些许的差异
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:49.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:50.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 稍有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:52.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,而它们中最出色的一辆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:54.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,叫做 GT3 RS
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.49,0:05:57.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以我想应该把它带到赛道上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:05:59.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,拉出来溜溜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:01.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,我真希望你在有生之年能有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.76,0:06:03.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,别表现的像个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:04.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,你这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.89,0:06:08.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,干脆直接说这车很烂 因为我有一辆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.50,0:06:12.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德 我是专业的汽车新闻工作者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:13.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,我要说...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:17.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,除了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:20.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,我将要提出我的专业观点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.81,0:06:27.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是我们讨论的车
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:30.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 等等 抱歉 稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:33.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,这有点容易搞混
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:34.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,这才是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:41.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,最火辣 最硬朗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:44.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,最紧凑的911
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:47.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,也是最梦幻的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:07:01.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,它的后胎是我在公路车中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:03.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,见过的最宽大的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:05.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,后面有防滚架增加刚性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:08.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,碳纤维的车身让它更轻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:11.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,车顶是用镁做成的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:13.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果你把车翻过来 车顶会磨出火花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.69,0:07:16.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,就会发出闪瞎眼的光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.13,0:07:17.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,于是你得到了一辆敞篷车
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:28.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,和很多人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:32.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,我并不欣赏911这种风格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:35.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且也不喜欢那些开这车的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:37.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,我觉得他们有些缺点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.07,0:07:39.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,在不为人知的那一面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:41.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,但我勉强承认
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:44.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,即使在最基本的驾驶模式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:47.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,开起来也十分惬意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.22,0:07:48.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,它们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:50.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,它们真的是很好的跑车
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.39,0:07:55.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,那这辆如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.73,0:07:57.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:07:59.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,让我们来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:08.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,实话实说 这台引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.66,0:08:10.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,实在太不可思议了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:14.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,没有涡轮增压
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.60,0:08:19.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,只是台4.0升的水平对置六缸机 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:22.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,它有500马力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.67,0:08:27.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,而它的转速红线是9000
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:34.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,9000转啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:36.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,那可是摩托车的标准
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:42.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,但最棒的是 它的过弯姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.11,0:08:46.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为它有四轮转向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:50.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,又因为引擎被放在了后轴正上方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:53.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,抓地力简直令人惊叹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:01.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,我开启了所有增强型按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:05.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,关闭所有辅助驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:09.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,看我还能否驾驭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:13.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,这里飞速驶入"斯文顿发春"弯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:19.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,并没有浪起来啊 这里很不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.11,0:09:22.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是 抓地力一点不少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:29.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,当我读参数表的时候 我以为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:32.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,保时捷要造一辆超跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:33.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,抗衡法拉利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:36.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,迈凯轮和兰博基尼 但是他们并没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.53,0:09:38.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,它仍是一辆跑车
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:41.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,它依然易操控 灵性十足
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:49.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,哇 它真的非常非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:50.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,真烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:10:00.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是它和这辆一样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:03.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,宝马 M4 GTS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.53,0:10:04.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,和保时捷一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:08.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,车身由特殊超轻材料制成的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.11,0:10:12.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,后排也被防滚架取而代之
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:14.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,还有超宽的轮胎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:18.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,看上去很美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:20.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,但存在一些问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.86,0:10:25.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,当你开着保时捷穿过减速带时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:28.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,电动升起车头 搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:33.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,但开着宝马 面对同样的减速带
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:38.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,你需要一堆人把前扰流板收起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:40.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,再升起车身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:42.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,这些要花上几个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:47.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且还有别的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:53.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,为了给车主一种驾驶赛车的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:56.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,所有的储物空间都被拆掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:10:59.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,没有扶手箱 没有储物槽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:01.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,没有什么地方放东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:03.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,我觉得从日常使用来讲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:05.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,绝对能把你逼疯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.86,0:11:12.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,至于驾乘感受 那是相当的颠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.68,0:11:16.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且轮胎的嗡嗡声 太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:21.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,在路上开了10分钟后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:22.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,你肯定会头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:25.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,而你却不能吃止痛药缓解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:27.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为没地儿放药啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:32.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,通常说到这里 我会说"然而"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:35.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,接着开始对车的优点侃侃而谈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.91,0:11:36.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:39.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,我做不到 因为
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:43.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,我实在找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:47.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,举个例子 这车有水喷射系统
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:50.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,听起来很酷炫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:53.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,但这意味着每加三次油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:56.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,就要给后备箱的水箱加水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:12:00.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,我虽然不懂 但我觉得这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:03.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,科技含量不高吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:07.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后说说转向
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:09.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,舒适模式下极其糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:12.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,然而在运动模式下更可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:16.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,即便如此 这个方向盘非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:18.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,它质感好又厚实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:22.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,就像握住了罗恩杰里米的那玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:24.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,座椅也不算太糟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:25.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,但除此之外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:28.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,没了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:31.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,有一点变得尤为明显
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.15,0:12:33.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,当你对阵保时捷的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:42.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,两车都有着差不多500马力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:45.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,都有着差不多304km/h的极速
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:49.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是保时捷要轻得多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.17,0:12:53.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,大概因为保时捷后备箱里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.03,0:12:55.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,没有装满水的水箱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:05.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,想跟上它都很难了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.56,0:13:09.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,来到了斯文顿弯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:11.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 原来是Springs啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:12.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,一家卖园艺的店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:15.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,啊 我要滑出去了 天啊 好险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:20.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,这车的反应可不够好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:24.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,对我这种野蛮的开车风格来说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:26.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,问题是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:31.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,就算谨慎小心的驾驶风格 它的反应也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:38.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,这两辆车之间的竞争
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:42.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,就像是一场专业拳击手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:45.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,和自认为是拳击手的人之间的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.78,0:13:48.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,只因为他们都穿丝绸裤衩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:16.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,宝马怎么把这车做得烂成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:18.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:23.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,它暴躁 难以预测
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:25.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且在雨里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:29.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,这车介于恶意满满和完全不能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:31.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,天哪 完全不能驾驶之间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:41.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,虽然如此 这车还是赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.82,0:14:44.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为理查德哈蒙德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:46.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,有这么一辆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:55.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,我就说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:56.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,太讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:14:58.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,这可是非常专业的测评
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:00.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,也就在几点上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:02.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是你本来做的挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.27,0:15:03.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,直到最后把结尾给搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:04.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.76,0:15:06.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,你选了最差的那辆车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:07.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为我没有买这辆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.00,0:15:10.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,-那辆保时捷伤了我 -伤你哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:11.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,确实伤了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:14.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为 你知道这车抓地力很强
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:15.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,以至于你有点被按在了椅子上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,然而座椅还有针脚在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.38,0:15:19.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,能把你后背磨个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:20.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,有图为证 它都干了什么 看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.03,0:15:22.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,那是我的后背
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:25.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,你居然没住院治疗 我好惊讶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:26.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:28.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,绝对的重伤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:29.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的车没这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.46,0:15:30.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为你是侏儒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:32.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,够不到那么高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:35.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,或者因为你就是怪胎 还坐错了地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.06,0:15:37.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,不仅是它会伤人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:40.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且保时捷比宝马贵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.97,0:15:44.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,对 但是我宁可花13万1千镑买个保时捷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:46.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,也不想花12万买个宝马
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.52,0:15:49.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,在公路和赛道上表现都不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:51.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且在雨里特别烂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:52.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 你说的都对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:54.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,-等等 -咋了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.09,0:15:56.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,我找到了宝马问题的根本所在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:15:57.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,就在这个广告上写着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:16:00.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,在纽博格林开发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:03.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,是啊 其实说道赛道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:06.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,是时候把M4交给
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:10.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,觉得气泡水基本就是共产党的哥们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:14.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,嗯 是时候把它交给那个美国佬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.84,0:16:17.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,他来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.65,0:16:20.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,他出发了 并没有出岔子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:22.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,排气因为升档发出了啪啪声
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:24.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,随着他驶入不直弯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:26.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,他知道自己在开什么车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:28.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,开宝马啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:31.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,不列颠汽车的结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:33.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,看来他并不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.75,0:16:36.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,接着攻入不直弯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:39.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们说这车马力更大了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:43.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,跟啥比的 我的电动牙刷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:45.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:48.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在向右驶入不直弯的末端
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.45,0:16:50.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,进入了留你名弯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:52.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,大脚刹车 把车保持在可控范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.87,0:16:54.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,我敢肯定他会感激
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.96,0:16:57.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,把他推出弯角的涡轮的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:16:58.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,引擎加了涡轮增压
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.82,0:17:02.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,就是老天爷告诉你气缸数量不够
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:04.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的错 好的 回到不直弯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:06.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,直六引擎全速运转
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:09.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,我不得不说 在外面听起来声浪很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:11.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,他开始大力转向
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:13.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,绕着哑弹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:16.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,进入了老奶房的窄弯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:20.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,踩油通过颠簸路段驶向地铁站
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.61,0:17:23.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,愚蠢的扰流板惊险的掠过车辙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:25.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在大脚踩下陶瓷刹车
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:27.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,通过狭窄的左弯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:30.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,轻轻给油 出弯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:32.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,再一次左弯来到羊圈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:36.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,稍微一点转向过度 然后冲过终点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:39.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,看走线很紧凑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.34,0:17:40.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,看着还行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:42.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,很紧凑 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:45.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,让我们打开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:46.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,让我们把圈速榜打开 如果可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.91,0:17:48.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在 我们看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:50.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们之前已经测试了911GT3RS
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:52.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,啥 你为啥不给我们看跑圈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:54.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,没人愿意看一个美国人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:17:57.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,被美化过的甲壳虫锯成两半
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:17:59.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,它跑了1分20秒4
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:18:01.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在我们看看M4的表现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:04.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,咱们把圈速放上去 就在这
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.86,0:18:08.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,慢了两秒  这还是个短赛道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:10.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,真是难以置信 这车不咋地 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:14.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,并不咋样 它只比保时捷718快了一秒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:16.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,我知道 我是说我钦佩宝马
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.73,0:18:19.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,为这辆车所做的努力 我真的这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:21.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是我的天啊 他们搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:23.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,事实上 我打算想一个暗喻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.55,0:18:27.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,为那些因为某些东西付出了最大努力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:28.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,却没有做到的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:36.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,没有 啥都没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:37.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:38.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,什么都没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.69,0:18:40.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以 让我们继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.96,0:18:44.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,是时候左转来到我们的唠嗑街
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.53,0:18:55.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,好的 我想从新福特GT说起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:57.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,这里有张它的图片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.89,0:19:00.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,你们记得上一款GT
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:03.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,那只是个对老GT40的致敬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.71,0:19:07.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,而这辆 他们说 是一辆真正的公路赛车
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.15,0:19:09.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,它有双涡轮 3.5升的V6引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:11.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,7速拨片换挡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:12.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,有超过600的马力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.95,0:19:17.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,问题是 我想不到任何的赛车
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.24,0:19:19.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,在公路上也适用 真的 从未
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:20.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,它们做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:23.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,我是说 尼桑GTR 一辆极好极好的车
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:26.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,在路上垃圾 完全不能开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:27.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,你知道 有个很好的观点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.98,0:19:29.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为在公路上的赛车
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:32.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,有点像用板球拍打网球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:33.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,技术上可行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:35.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,但完全是两个规则
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.66,0:19:39.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,问题是这辆车看起来太棒了 我觉得我要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:43.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,那个 你买了上一代福特GT对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:44.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:47.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,谢谢你提醒我 哈蒙德 我买了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:49.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,-开得还好么 -不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.42,0:19:51.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,-噢 是吗 -对 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:52.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,问题在于保险公司说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:54.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,我必须要装个报警器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:55.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,每次我女儿排校园剧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:58.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,报警就乱叫 然后毁了排练
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.31,0:19:59.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且还得配追踪器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:03.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,这世上没什么比追踪器更讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:05.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,我就有个 一点也没烦到我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:07.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为你会在门厅桌上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:09.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,有个位置专门放它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:12.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,带上钥匙 别忘了还有追踪器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.70,0:20:14.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为你有条理 而我没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:15.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,这里是追踪器 这里是钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:17.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,这里是你的小铅笔刀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.03,0:20:18.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,一些零钱 以备不时之需
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.04,0:20:20.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,-没错 10便士的 2便士的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.68,0:20:22.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,还有一个修眼镜的小螺丝刀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:23.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,-他真会这样 -我才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.98,0:20:26.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,不是 它一直被放在一个小袋子里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:27.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,直接挂到钥匙链上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.65,0:20:28.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,-谁信啊 -你还有个小袋子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:31.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,他还给追踪器配了个袋子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:32.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,是专门放追踪器的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.72,0:20:34.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,-当然了 因为 -什么材质的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:37.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我记得是皮的 -一个小皮袋子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:38.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,是你亲手做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.87,0:20:40.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,-不 它是 -那个小皮袋子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:42.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,它是随车赠送的 爱信不信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:44.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,这么说是法拉利卖给你的喽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:47.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,多少钱 我猜是600镑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:48.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,没有 真是随车赠送的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:50.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,我才不信法拉利有这么大方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.24,0:20:51.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,你那辆法拉利上面的条纹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:53.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,那两道条纹 跟福特上面的有点像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:56.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,就那两道 你花了多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:20:58.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,那个是选配项 6000镑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.27,0:21:03.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,你看 所以说我开是高尔夫GTI
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.52,0:21:04.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为你不需要报警器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.97,0:21:05.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,也不需要追踪器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:07.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且比上一代GTI
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:09.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,低了五个保险等级
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:11.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,-哇 -真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:13.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为你不会撞坏它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:15.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,我肯定能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.43,0:21:18.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.83,0:21:20.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,你们知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:22.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,特拉法加广场上面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:23.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,新装的行人信号灯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:26.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,在美国的观众朋友们 说的是英国伦敦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.40,0:21:27.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,是那个 噢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.04,0:21:31.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,是上面有两俩男人的信号灯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.41,0:21:33.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯 你这是性别歧视
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.28,0:21:35.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,-怎么就 -如果你是女同性恋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.58,0:21:38.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,那就换两个女人上去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:40.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果你是直的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.35,0:21:43.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,-一男一女 -但是信号灯只有这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.14,0:21:45.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,你不可能同时显示两男人 一男一女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.31,0:21:47.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,一个不确定性别的 再加上两女人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.86,0:21:52.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果 如果你只是想过马路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.07,0:21:55.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,你们两个简直还活在70年代
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.40,0:21:58.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在过马路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.28,0:22:00.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,是展现自己性征的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:01.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,就是 所以他们才会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:04.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,在伦敦装这种信号灯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.17,0:22:05.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是做什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.49,0:22:07.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,相信我 他们装了 真的装了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.57,0:22:09.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,-是真的吗 -都是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.27,0:22:11.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,右边那个是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.33,0:22:13.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,当然是变性人群体了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.43,0:22:17.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,什么 等一下 只有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.19,0:22:18.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,-没错 -怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.97,0:22:20.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,跨性别者信号灯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.79,0:22:23.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我还真不知道 -所以只有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:26.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,只有变性人才能在它变绿的时候过马路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.27,0:22:27.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.60,0:22:29.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,那当它变红的时候 是否就意味着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.30,0:22:31.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,跨性别是不被允许的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.19,0:22:32.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,说得好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.77,0:22:34.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,我也不知道变红的时候是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.41,0:22:36.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们肯定不能说 呃 我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:40.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,那这些跟过马路有关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.20,0:22:41.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,你只想过马路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.29,0:22:43.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,不是为了展现性征
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.04,0:22:45.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,这不是展现的时候 我只想过马路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.17,0:22:45.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,我在信号灯变绿的时候 心里想的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:48.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,就是该如何跨到那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.52,0:22:50.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,我刚刚的意思不是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.08,0:22:53.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,我不是那意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.07,0:22:55.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.94,0:22:58.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,路的那一边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.65,0:23:00.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,没准你是对的 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.67,0:23:02.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,好了 我可以聊两句阿尔法罗密欧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.04,0:23:04.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,-不行 -为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.59,0:23:06.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为接下来该介绍我们的影片了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.44,0:23:09.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,众所周知 近些年各大汽车厂商
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.21,0:23:11.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,在研发更经济和环境友好型
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.98,0:23:14.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,的发动机方面成果显著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.65,0:23:16.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,但在制造更加环保的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.42,0:23:19.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,车身和内饰方面下的功夫却很少
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.69,0:23:23.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,没错 总的来说还是以钢材和塑料为主
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.09,0:23:25.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,而这会消耗很多的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.29,0:23:26.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,于是我们就有个了想法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.49,0:23:30.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,能不能把它们替换成其他永续材料呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.30,0:23:33.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,为了验证这点 我们每个人都买了一辆路虎发现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.90,0:23:36.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,去掉它们的金属车身
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:40.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,并替换成我们认为能够保护地球的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.51,0:23:42.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,最佳解决方案
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.85,0:23:48.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,集合点选在了威尔士
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.02,0:23:51.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,我是第一个到的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.45,0:23:53.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,开着一辆泥巴做的车
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.67,0:24:01.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,可惜我还没来得及做介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.56,0:24:02.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.27,0:24:13.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,让我来讲讲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.84,0:24:17.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,我用榛木搭了个框架
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.18,0:24:19.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,中间穿插编制着许多英国的花卉和灌木
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.01,0:24:21.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,基本上就是个灌木篱墙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.55,0:24:23.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,更妙的是 这些都是我种的 它们还会生长
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.72,0:24:27.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,这里有肥料和土壤给它们提供营养
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.12,0:24:29.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,让我的车生机盎然
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.29,0:24:31.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,你并不是在洗车
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.07,0:24:32.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,而是在给它浇水
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.41,0:24:34.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,它是活的 多棒的主意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.83,0:24:37.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,-还长了铁线莲 -修剪过的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.43,0:24:38.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,你在向嬉皮士靠拢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.81,0:24:41.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 但我觉得有这种趋势
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.27,0:24:42.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你的呢 -那个
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.80,0:24:44.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,可惜 我还没来得及说
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.87,0:24:47.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,杰瑞米就来了 画风有点不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.35,0:24:59.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,先生们 我知道会发生啥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.19,0:25:03.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,看到了我的天才作品之后
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.02,0:25:07.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,你们会惊讶的说不出话来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.79,0:25:11.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,一辆用骨头和皮做成的车
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.30,0:25:13.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,-什么骨头 -动物骨头
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.87,0:25:15.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,骨头不是这样用的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.19,0:25:16.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,你不能拿它来造车
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.99,0:25:18.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,为什么不行 比如说你的狗死了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.81,0:25:20.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,你怎么办 把它埋了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.24,0:25:22.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,-那也不会把它做成行引擎盖 -为什么不
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.44,0:25:24.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为我不想看到它的小脸被拉成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.72,0:25:27.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,不用脸皮 我也没用脸皮
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.48,0:25:29.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,只是骨头
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.47,0:25:31.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以当奶奶岁数大了 家人会商量
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.58,0:25:33.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,改造一台小掀背吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.95,0:25:35.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,我暂时还没考虑用人骨
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.42,0:25:37.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,好像有点不尊重死者
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.79,0:25:39.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,你是不是用耳朵做了后视镜
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.49,0:25:40.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,-是的 -你太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.93,0:25:43.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,为什么不呢 物尽其用
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.20,0:25:45.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,-才不是呢 -本来就是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.70,0:25:46.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,耳朵并不反光
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.81,0:25:50.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,耳朵可以收集信息并传递给生物
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.24,0:25:51.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,-看我的挡风玻璃 -这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.01,0:25:54.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是 一头牛的消化系统
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.14,0:25:56.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,消化系统的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.81,0:25:58.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,哪部分
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.24,0:26:00.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,-是胃粘膜 -不是胃粘膜
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.38,0:26:02.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,-那是什么 再往后吗 -对
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.25,0:26:04.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,你是通过一头牛的屁眼来观察前方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.42,0:26:09.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,这确实是牛的肛门
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.32,0:26:11.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,但被拉扯得很薄
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.05,0:26:14.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,已经完全透明了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.08,0:26:15.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,牛的屁眼 马的屁眼 真是辆好车
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.98,0:26:20.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,比你们两个强多了 你们简直一无是处
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.47,0:26:23.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,-这车是用什么做的 -你猜 -是泥巴
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.20,0:26:24.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,没错 这是辆泥巴车
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.87,0:26:26.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你的轮胎没气了 -不是没气
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.61,0:26:29.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,是接近爆胎的最高胎压了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.53,0:26:31.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,-这车有多沉 -很沉
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.21,0:26:32.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,-多沉 -很沉
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.65,0:26:34.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯 它到底多沉
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.38,0:26:35.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你想用什么单位 -吨
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.02,0:26:37.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,五
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.72,0:26:41.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,-5吨? 你傻啊 -泥巴很重的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.62,0:26:42.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,这车看起来很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.99,0:26:45.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,同时还很环保 植物都在生长
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.10,0:26:47.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,就在我们讲话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.15,0:26:48.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,这辆车又长了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.79,0:26:50.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,-它会默默地成长 -这辆车是活的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.85,0:26:51.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,所有东西都种在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.85,0:26:54.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,我把浇水用浇斗放在这儿了 这是水仙花
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.17,0:26:56.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,-不安全吧 -榛木 结实得很
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.90,0:26:58.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,并没有骨头结实
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.59,0:27:01.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,骨头比钢材还要硬三倍
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.36,0:27:02.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.48,0:27:05.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢抱歉 有短信
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.28,0:27:06.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,韦尔曼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.05,0:27:08.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,在用天然材料造好车之后
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.98,0:27:10.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,你们要将其驶回大自然
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.02,0:27:12.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,开到玛雅丘陵去
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.66,0:27:16.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,在那里你们将会参与一场环保汽车比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.12,0:27:18.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,-什么环保汽车比赛 -他没说
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.93,0:27:23.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,可能是某种程度上比较环保的比赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.16,0:27:24.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.23,0:27:25.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,在出发之前
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.59,0:27:28.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们拿出地图来研究一番
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.90,0:27:31.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,看 这是英国
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.37,0:27:34.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们在这儿 而终点在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.28,0:27:39.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,看上去毫无难度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.73,0:27:42.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,看完地图 我们准备出发
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.89,0:27:46.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,开始这趟史诗般的18公里旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.82,0:27:49.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧这烟
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.34,0:27:50.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,非常环保
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.76,0:27:54.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,绿色和平组织会随时给他打电话的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.59,0:27:56.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.36,0:27:58.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,呼吸自然 坐拥自然
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.03,0:28:01.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,大自然造就了我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.50,0:28:02.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,车速并不快
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.98,0:28:06.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,正好给了我时间去享受上帝的杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.44,0:28:09.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,我本人也是其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.24,0:28:11.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.54,0:28:14.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.52,0:28:22.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们才开始了10秒 詹姆斯却
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.06,0:28:24.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,专业点说就是
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.59,0:28:26.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,A柱要掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.16,0:28:29.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在完全掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.87,0:28:33.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢 天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.10,0:28:39.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,他必须得认输了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.64,0:28:41.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,他那辆车已经没剩多少了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.84,0:28:44.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,天呐 詹姆斯
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.78,0:28:46.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,我觉得你已经可以出局了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.35,0:28:47.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,-可这无所谓啊 -什么无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.78,0:28:50.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,你会这么想 噢詹姆斯的车散架了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.12,0:28:54.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,我正站在配件库里 到处都是配件
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.22,0:28:56.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,可以用来重建你的车
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.28,0:28:57.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,-就在我们脚下 泥巴
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.22,0:28:59.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,像新的一样 -算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.80,0:29:03.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我们要继续前进 把你扔在这儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.70,0:29:05.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,等一下 你不能走
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.07,0:29:06.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为我们还没开始呢 我们还在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.57,0:29:07.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,-也是 -好吧 那这样
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.95,0:29:10.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们出发去找个酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.70,0:29:12.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,-好主意 -你就
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.64,0:29:15.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,-在这里 -挖泥巴
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.54,0:29:18.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,我找不到我的车了 噢 在这儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.68,0:29:21.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,把巴布工程师扔下之后
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.61,0:29:23.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,理查德和我开始认真享受
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.82,0:29:28.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们生态汽车的环保属性
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.92,0:29:31.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,你可能会
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.79,0:29:33.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,笑话我的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.29,0:29:35.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,或是被吓到
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.53,0:29:40.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,但要知道用钢材制作车身的话
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.33,0:29:46.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,每年会产生1.2亿吨的二氧化碳
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.64,0:29:49.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,1.2亿吨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.08,0:29:53.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,汽车厂商们早晚会制造出
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.15,0:29:55.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,环境友好型的发动机 我相信他们
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.88,0:29:57.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,与此同时
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.10,0:30:00.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,我这辆车所排出的二氧化碳
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.40,0:30:04.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,都会被车身吸收并加以利用
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.66,0:30:08.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为植物可以吸入二氧化碳 释放出氧气
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.94,0:30:12.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,而我的车身此时就在做这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.53,0:30:17.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,套头衫 吃大餐 满地都是小配件
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.03,0:30:21.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,你不需要用车间和熔炉
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.12,0:30:22.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,来造车
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.78,0:30:26.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,只需要小动物们互相交配就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.26,0:30:30.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,这车的本质就是个性爱机器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.59,0:30:35.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,与此同时 大本营那边 詹姆斯换了个思路
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.07,0:30:38.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,我决定放弃我原先的方案
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.60,0:30:41.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为泥巴实在是太松太软了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.05,0:30:44.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以我打算要用砖头造一辆车
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.24,0:30:46.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,制作砖头的原料主要有
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.14,0:30:49.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,带点水的新鲜泥土
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.42,0:30:52.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,少许稻草 让其更加坚固
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.54,0:30:54.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,还有羊粪
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.65,0:30:57.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,用这些做成砖头的形状
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.33,0:30:59.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后放到窑里去烧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.13,0:31:01.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后你就可以用烧出来的砖去盖房子了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.70,0:31:04.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,只不过我们这次是要盖个车子出来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.57,0:31:11.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,说回在路上的人 哈蒙德叫停了我们的环保车队
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.14,0:31:13.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,-怎么了 -嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.65,0:31:15.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,嘘什么
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.33,0:31:17.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的篱笆下面有声音
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.51,0:31:20.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,不要惊慌
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.88,0:31:25.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,-这只是个大扫除 -什么 要迎接春姑娘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.67,0:31:29.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,原来 我车上还有位乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.00,0:31:32.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,等等 在那 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.18,0:31:34.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,是只刺猬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.51,0:31:36.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,对 它搬进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.41,0:31:40.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,刺猬有骨头吗 能否用来做后视镜
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.13,0:31:42.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,他现在是我小小社区的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.74,0:31:44.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,你不能用他做后视镜
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.79,0:31:46.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我是说等他死了 -他就在这住
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.58,0:31:48.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,刺猬终有一死
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.81,0:32:12.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,喔 他还在鸟笼子里养了只老鼠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.61,0:32:16.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,这我见过最大的老鼠蛋蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.65,0:32:21.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,终于 我和理查德抵达了酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.31,0:32:27.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,不是吧 你是不是傻
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.34,0:32:31.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,自己看
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.34,0:32:33.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,彻底掉了 没法修 除非用销子
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.40,0:32:36.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,闭嘴 你那车都让我花粉过敏了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.57,0:32:37.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,瞎了我的眼
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.00,0:32:40.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以 你撞车是因为我车上种着花
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.98,0:32:42.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,而不是因为你挡风玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.81,0:32:44.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,是用牛菊花做的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.29,0:32:46.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们就别纠结这个事故是谁错了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.78,0:32:47.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,反正是你
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.70,0:32:49.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,我得去找点备用零件了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.99,0:32:50.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,对 那太容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.90,0:32:53.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,这个小村庄或许就会有个不错的动物园
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.14,0:32:54.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 医院也行 养老院
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.75,0:32:57.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,哎等会 你就去找个那样的老太太
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.19,0:33:00.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,而在起点
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.70,0:33:03.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们的环保卫士则开足了马力
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.50,0:33:25.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,等着瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.88,0:33:28.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,与此同时 在酒吧这边
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.73,0:33:31.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,我正在修理损坏的车头
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.17,0:33:35.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,比较烦的是 我买的猪肉
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.13,0:33:37.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,是三角形的 看起来不太对
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.11,0:33:39.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,不大合适 所以我买了块牛骨
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.77,0:33:41.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,我觉得会很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.23,0:33:43.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,让我先把原来的骨头弄下来
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.85,0:33:54.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,走开 走开的威尔士语
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.44,0:33:56.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,我警告你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.44,0:34:00.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,我会把你做成油箱盖的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.15,0:34:05.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.73,0:34:07.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,我反正觉得这造型挺有范的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.35,0:34:11.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,一看就特环保特可回收
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.51,0:34:13.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,符合可持续发展等等
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.58,0:34:16.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,有了这么一块砖门
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.38,0:34:18.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,工艺精湛 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.81,0:34:21.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,这和乐高其实是一个原理
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.74,0:34:24.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,当然 你得有很多乐高积木
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.38,0:34:32.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.14,0:34:37.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,很明显 詹姆斯当天是不可能完成他的车了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.30,0:34:41.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以理查德和我打算在酒吧过夜
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.33,0:34:44.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,告诉我 今天咱们走了多远
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.30,0:34:46.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们还在开始的那块地方
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.26,0:34:47.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,-他还在那 -没错
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.56,0:34:50.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我们在酒吧  -但我们得回起点重新开始
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.33,0:34:54.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,-这次开局不利 -对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.50,0:34:56.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道呢 我们也还没开始啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.75,0:34:59.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,没错 所以等真开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.17,0:35:01.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,没准是个非常棒的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.70,0:35:14.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,他那破玩意就是废物
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.15,0:35:16.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,都怪他做事粗糙
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.88,0:35:18.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,还钻牛角尖
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.54,0:35:19.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,谢谢各位
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.41,0:35:23.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在又是我们的明星脑碰脑环节
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.08,0:35:32.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,上周
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.49,0:35:34.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,上周 大家肯定还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.15,0:35:36.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们的嘉宾西蒙佩吉
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.56,0:35:39.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,不幸跌入河里溺水身亡
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.19,0:35:42.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,但这周就不会再有这个危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.19,0:35:45.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为本期嘉宾就从水上出发的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.65,0:35:48.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,他是英国的一位顶级笑星
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.56,0:35:50.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,也是一位摩托艇爱好者
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.01,0:35:55.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,各位 掌声有请吉米卡尔
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.71,0:35:58.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,看大屏幕 他这就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.01,0:36:01.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,他看上去神采奕奕
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.06,0:36:03.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,没错 等他来了我们问人家点什么好
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.88,0:36:06.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,我要问他
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.42,0:36:08.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们一起度假时 他和我说过一次的那个事
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.56,0:36:10.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 你不能在节目上问那事
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.49,0:36:12.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,有关部门不会允许的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.22,0:36:13.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,有他们什么事 我们这是网络节目
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.89,0:36:17.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,但节目还是要播的 你不能提那事
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.28,0:36:20.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.30,0:36:22.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,我不是有意打断 但是他速度有点太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.79,0:36:26.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,那船怎么回事 各位 安静
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.18,0:36:27.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,快叫停这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.74,0:36:29.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,天呐 要撞上了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.02,0:36:33.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的天老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.10,0:36:52.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,各位可能注意到 现场观众们
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.19,0:36:59.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,在为英国人挚爱的喜剧明星吉米卡尔之死鼓掌
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.58,0:37:03.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,那他是来不成了?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.11,0:37:05.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯 他已经炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.81,0:37:08.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,掉河里喂鱼了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.94,0:37:11.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以 不 他来不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.34,0:37:12.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,这真是... 尴尬了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.01,0:37:13.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,每周都如此
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.92,0:37:15.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们会臭名远扬 大家会发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.95,0:37:16.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.87,0:37:21.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,我想到可以用什么桥段来补了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.57,0:37:22.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,你懂得
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.88,0:37:25.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你先出去 还有你 -能不做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.30,0:37:27.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,不行 快过去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.62,0:37:29.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,把那玩意弄过来 快快快 跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.60,0:37:31.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.06,0:37:33.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,尽量别去看窗外的河面
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.18,0:37:35.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,水面上可怕的血迹
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.37,0:37:38.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.39,0:37:41.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,当移民们偷渡入境时
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.70,0:37:44.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们都会藏在集装箱卡车里
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.28,0:37:45.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,我一直觉得这是世上
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.49,0:37:47.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,最白痴的躲猫猫了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.86,0:37:50.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果你是国土安全局的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.01,0:37:50.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,等等 英国叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.96,0:37:52.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,边防部队
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.65,0:37:54.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,边防一开门就 抓到你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.03,0:37:56.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以我想
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.89,0:38:00.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,肯定还有比这更好的偷渡方式
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.45,0:38:03.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且我觉得找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.51,0:38:06.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,-詹姆斯 把车开进来  -好
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.67,0:38:07.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,好样的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.69,0:38:09.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,好的 他来了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.27,0:38:11.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,以他的日常龟速
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.04,0:38:15.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,开着一辆奥迪TT四驱
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.72,0:38:17.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,太棒了 谢谢你詹姆斯
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.14,0:38:18.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,在请你下车
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.61,0:38:23.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,理查德哈蒙德就在这辆车里
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.49,0:38:27.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,现场的观众们 我给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.42,0:38:28.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,一个小时找到他
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.81,0:38:30.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,一小时太长了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.43,0:38:31.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧不一小时 一分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.93,0:38:34.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,给你们60秒钟找到他
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.12,0:38:36.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,各位自便 看看自己能否找到他
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.67,0:38:38.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,-打开引擎盖 -烟灰缸里面
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.80,0:38:42.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,烟灰缸里面 他是迷你了点但也还没那么小
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.21,0:38:44.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,-打开后备箱  -座位夹层
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.55,0:38:46.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,座位夹层吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.28,0:38:48.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,他被绑在车底 他在底下
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.21,0:38:50.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你自己看 -我躺下看看
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.32,0:38:52.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,你蹲下去就能看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.45,0:38:53.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,有人把这个打开看过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.86,0:38:56.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,三 二 一
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.39,0:38:57.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,你们都失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.06,0:39:00.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,千万别去移民局工作
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.28,0:39:04.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,都回到自己的位置上 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.89,0:39:07.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们现在要来告诉大家
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.91,0:39:11.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,理查德哈蒙德到底藏在哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.61,0:39:13.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯 搭把手
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.51,0:39:15.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,-没问题  -好的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.96,0:39:17.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,-大家好  -在这呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.61,0:39:21.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,大家好 我真的在车里 你没看没错
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.33,0:39:25.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.93,0:39:28.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,还行 我能出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.35,0:39:31.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,最神奇的是 如果你想要贩卖人口
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.79,0:39:34.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,不仅是奥迪TT
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.41,0:39:36.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,几乎所有的车都有块这么大的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.59,0:39:39.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,讲真 这空间也没有那么大
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.46,0:39:40.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,我能出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.80,0:39:43.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,不行 我又想到一个事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.83,0:39:45.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,真的 詹姆斯 你能把保险杠装回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.82,0:39:47.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,什么 动下腿
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.61,0:39:49.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,-因为  -兄弟情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.01,0:39:53.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,那是什么 先把这装回去
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.31,0:39:55.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在这就是
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.31,0:39:59.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,一个特管用的倒车雷达
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.20,0:40:02.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,-什么 我不要啊  -好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.83,0:40:06.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,你坐回去 我去找辆车进来
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.19,0:40:07.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,做倒车参照物
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.03,0:40:10.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,我还要给你开两个观察口
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.24,0:40:12.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,你敢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.73,0:40:14.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德 说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.74,0:40:17.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,这样你才看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.10,0:40:18.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,你的眼睛在哪 这吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.49,0:40:19.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,在我脑袋上
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.75,0:40:21.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,好的 哈蒙德 闭上眼
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.38,0:40:33.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你还活着吗 -我不理你了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.07,0:40:37.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,还要帮另外一只眼打个孔
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.14,0:40:42.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,搞定 能看得到外面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.26,0:40:45.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,快看 多棒 你能看到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.36,0:40:47.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们能看到他的小眼睛呢 真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.04,0:40:48.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,帮我拿一下
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.49,0:40:51.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯 倒车的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.37,0:40:54.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,请竖起耳朵听哈蒙德的惨叫
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.84,0:40:55.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.04,0:40:58.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,不要 停
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.50,0:41:00.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 停
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.41,0:41:03.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,还有多远-大概5米
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.15,0:41:05.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,-什么-哈蒙德
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.56,0:41:07.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,干嘛-我们住在伦敦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.35,0:41:10.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,这距离可以建个四百万英镑的房子了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.52,0:41:12.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,只剩2厘米再叫
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.56,0:41:15.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,你来这要命的保险杠里试试
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.48,0:41:17.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,-好了 继续吧詹姆斯 -走着
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.70,0:41:20.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德 没有生命危险就保持安静
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.30,0:41:28.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.97,0:41:32.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,真是完美
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.83,0:41:35.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,只有不到1厘米了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.62,0:41:37.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.06,0:41:39.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,哇!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.89,0:41:44.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,问题是 倒车雷达十分昂贵
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.20,0:41:46.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,找个活人却是免费的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.25,0:41:49.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,我不知道你平时找别人出多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.59,0:41:51.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,但我身价很高
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.32,0:41:53.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在 请放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.41,0:41:56.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,不行 是时候继续节目了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.19,0:41:58.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们也无法让你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.97,0:41:59.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为两辆车太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.70,0:42:00.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,没法卸下保险杠
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.77,0:42:03.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,-哈蒙德 你活太棒了  -去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.73,0:42:05.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,就是这样 该回到正题了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.94,0:42:08.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,到第二段了 我们刚刚到哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.79,0:42:11.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,-意大利那段吗 -不 那是上周的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.86,0:42:14.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,-是说车呢 -是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.94,0:42:16.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,环境友好型汽车
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.13,0:42:18.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,对 可持续车辆 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.93,0:42:24.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,快继续啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.21,0:42:29.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,隔天一早 我们精神抖擞地早早起床
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.76,0:42:32.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,重新回到起点
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.61,0:42:37.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,-昨晚睡的不错呢  -还行
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.01,0:42:39.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,你好 小伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.94,0:42:42.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯快来看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.31,0:42:48.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,看来狗和狐狸对你的车情有独钟
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.55,0:42:50.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,狗把你的车给吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.03,0:42:53.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,没有吃 只是毁了我的车
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.36,0:42:56.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以我还得把这重新归位
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.73,0:42:59.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,那有些零件
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.42,0:43:02.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,那马确实看起来病得不轻
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.69,0:43:04.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,脸色苍白
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.44,0:43:06.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,这往往意味着生病了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.20,0:43:08.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,你的马病了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.37,0:43:09.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,-没  -居然没有
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.89,0:43:11.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,-就是说它能活过今天了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.35,0:43:12.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,-没错
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.31,0:43:16.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.29,0:43:21.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,我花了一早上
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.19,0:43:22.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,用肉店买的零件修车
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.99,0:43:24.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以我们回程
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.99,0:43:26.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,去看詹姆斯进展如何时
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.22,0:43:29.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,已经是中午了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.89,0:43:33.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,杰里米 前面的烟是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.15,0:43:35.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,什么烟
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.70,0:43:38.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,就是前面的浓烟 看那
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.01,0:43:41.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,看不见 我严重花粉过敏
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.66,0:43:43.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 是因为你得通过牛的菊花
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.39,0:43:45.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,才能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.49,0:43:49.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,结果证明 这烟源于詹姆斯
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.31,0:43:55.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,一手重启的工业革命
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.59,0:44:03.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,-怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.10,0:44:04.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你在干什么  -我在...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.65,0:44:13.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们的目的是减少对环境的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.64,0:44:15.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,但你把地球都挖空了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.11,0:44:16.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,这地渺无人烟
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.13,0:44:18.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是郊外 不会影响到谁
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.24,0:44:19.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,那是运煤车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.78,0:44:23.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,-嗯  -那是地球上最不环保的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.28,0:44:26.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,那是辆运煤的卡车
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.28,0:44:28.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,-所以呢  -你要煤干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.59,0:44:30.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,-给窖生火  -什么
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.76,0:44:32.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,砖块是烧出来的 你不能就这么...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.92,0:44:36.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,-等等 你要用砖块造车吗  -没错
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.99,0:44:38.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,你为了运煤
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.65,0:44:40.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是要挖条运河吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.38,0:44:42.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,-好主意  -才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.12,0:44:46.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,蹂躏完郊区后
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.84,0:44:50.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯的车终于造好了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.54,0:44:53.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,你为什么穿得像个橄榄球运动员
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.26,0:44:55.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,这车还只是个雏形
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.22,0:44:57.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,我是来试驾的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.39,0:44:59.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,试驾员通常需要一些特殊装备
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.63,0:45:02.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,我看那挺结实的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.81,0:45:04.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,那车顶简直...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.24,0:45:08.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯 光想想你用的原材料的局限性
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.21,0:45:09.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,这车就烂透了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.59,0:45:11.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是它和这环境特别配
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.63,0:45:13.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,查尔斯王子肯定会很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.15,0:45:14.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,它和什么都不配
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.33,0:45:17.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,这已经没有环境可言 因为你都挖出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.12,0:45:19.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,-行吧 我们可以开动了吗  -当然
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.84,0:45:22.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,前面还有18公里要走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.71,0:45:24.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,终点见
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.03,0:45:28.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.31,0:45:37.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,我就不明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.61,0:45:39.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.28,0:45:41.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,这个拱顶还带拱心石呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.03,0:45:44.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,肯定是砂浆的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.64,0:45:47.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,等待詹姆斯再次修理车体时
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.82,0:45:50.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的车正在逐渐消失
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.39,0:45:56.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,但最终 他准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.94,0:46:03.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,驾驶感不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.42,0:46:06.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,就像在家开着窗户一样
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.49,0:46:10.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,同时 理查德给他的车种上了赛车条纹
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.66,0:46:12.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,我也卸下了牛的直肠
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.97,0:46:15.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,来通风
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.38,0:46:19.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们是出过问题
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.51,0:46:23.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,没错 三公里走了两天
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.21,0:46:25.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,但我们的三人行
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.31,0:46:28.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,还在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.91,0:46:35.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.51,0:46:38.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,前面是条挺大的河
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.13,0:46:45.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,夭寿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.80,0:46:50.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的天老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.83,0:46:52.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,哥们你的砖块在往下掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.65,0:46:54.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,引擎盖掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.13,0:46:56.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,没事 我多铺了一层
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.74,0:46:58.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,-是吗  -真的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.96,0:47:01.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,由于理查德是我们队的乡巴佬
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.37,0:47:04.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们决定让他先走
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.74,0:47:07.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的盟友们
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.88,0:47:09.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,向着高处走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.04,0:47:10.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,往上爬
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.06,0:47:14.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德方舟最终成功靠岸
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.55,0:47:16.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,耶
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.46,0:47:18.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在该我了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.34,0:47:21.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,这里好深
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.54,0:47:23.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,真的好深
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.18,0:47:25.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,牛车进水了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.76,0:47:28.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,这可是个深刻的教训
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.09,0:47:32.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,但我也相对轻松地到岸了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.47,0:47:34.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德 你服不服!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.08,0:47:36.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,但
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.03,0:47:38.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,看看他
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.90,0:47:40.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.20,0:47:43.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,老家伙开着一堵花园墙下河
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.97,0:47:45.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,好消息是
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.41,0:47:47.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,这车如果抛锚了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.26,0:47:49.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,还可以当大坝
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.35,0:47:55.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,他这速度比咱们慢多了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.03,0:47:58.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,也不够强势 太盲目了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.54,0:48:01.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为这重量
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.55,0:48:02.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,车身也更低
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.97,0:48:06.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,正在往深水区前进 有点漏水了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.17,0:48:09.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,漏水很严重
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.07,0:48:14.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,糟糕 伙计们我这是搁浅了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.73,0:48:17.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,讲真 我们也无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.36,0:48:19.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,你在河里 我们却在岸上
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.58,0:48:21.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 如果我往右走一点
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.83,0:48:24.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,我就能走出去
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.76,0:48:26.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.05,0:48:29.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,-车门掉下来了  -不忍直视
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.83,0:48:31.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,砂浆在水里溶解了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.21,0:48:32.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且砖块也在往下掉
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.64,0:48:33.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.14,0:48:37.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,又掉了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.74,0:48:40.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,天啊 砂浆在溶解
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.57,0:48:43.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,等他开过来 估计散的只剩摄像机了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.24,0:48:44.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,绝对散架了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.55,0:48:45.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,下去
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.14,0:48:49.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,下去
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.71,0:48:52.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,纤弱的手臂 扔着砖块
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.90,0:48:55.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.53,0:48:59.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们得赶紧帮他结束这痛苦的行程
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.88,0:49:02.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,应该直接抛弃他 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.88,0:49:05.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,要他何用
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.26,0:49:06.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯 听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.93,0:49:09.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们评估了一下现在的情形
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.03,0:49:12.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们确实爱莫能助 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.43,0:49:15.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,抛弃了詹姆斯和他正在溶解的车后
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.02,0:49:20.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们继续前行扎营 准备晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.06,0:49:24.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,除了你那可怜的帐篷外
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.16,0:49:26.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,-这还挺不错的  -是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.21,0:49:29.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,我车看起来真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.32,0:49:32.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,它和树篱融为一体了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.37,0:49:35.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,不止是伪装 那就是个树篱
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.56,0:49:37.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我的车已经消失了  -它真的...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.35,0:49:41.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,我同意 你的车确实别出心裁
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.57,0:49:46.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,另一边 詹姆斯的车大量减重
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.14,0:49:48.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,终于重获自由
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.62,0:49:53.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,他又开始劫掠大自然来重造车体
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.44,0:49:54.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.80,0:50:00.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,我跟你说 我们现在这种
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.62,0:50:03.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,可持续生活的亮点在于-
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.26,0:50:07.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,烤肉用的砖是詹姆斯车上的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.53,0:50:11.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,引火物和蔬菜是你车上的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.89,0:50:14.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,难道说我正在吃的是
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.33,0:50:16.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的后翼子板
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.09,0:50:23.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,-怎么了 -你买的牛排上面都会写着冷藏保存
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.84,0:50:25.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,不会有人让你把它贴在车的侧面
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.62,0:50:28.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,在阳光下暴晒 再开过一条河
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.58,0:50:49.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯搞出的噪音真是太讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.66,0:50:51.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,比上次还讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.40,0:50:56.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,不同之处在于 这次他一直在破坏大自然
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.23,0:50:59.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,我可不像他那样
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.24,0:51:01.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,他只会把所有事情都搞砸 一向如此
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.40,0:51:09.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.26,0:51:10.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,-哈蒙德 -怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.63,0:51:14.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.44,0:51:18.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.06,0:51:19.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,他开着篱笆修剪机看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.68,0:51:22.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,那可是我的小生态 你个混蛋乡巴佬
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.96,0:51:26.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,-噢 -噢天呐
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.15,0:51:30.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,第二天一早
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.35,0:51:32.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,为了让受到双重打击的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.49,0:51:35.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈蒙德高兴一点
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.19,0:51:37.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,我做了早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.06,0:51:40.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,-吃吧 -不
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.34,0:51:42.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,-为什么 -因为它都变质了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.34,0:51:43.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,只是门上的一块肉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.02,0:51:45.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,你可以看出上面曾经落过苍蝇
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.82,0:51:47.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,太恶心了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.14,0:51:48.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧谁来了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.66,0:51:49.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.90,0:51:53.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,-那是个粪堆 -确实是个粪堆
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.07,0:51:58.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,-早上好 -早
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.44,0:52:00.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是一辆车还是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.05,0:52:04.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是一辆用抹灰篱笆墙造的可持续发展汽车
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.27,0:52:06.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,只不过我把篱笆换成了稻草
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.23,0:52:08.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,又把石灰换成了牛粪
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.49,0:52:09.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,但道理是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.99,0:52:12.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你到底是怎么进去的 -刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.69,0:52:14.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,-挡风玻璃呢 -在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.86,0:52:15.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.20,0:52:19.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们来测试一下你的盲区吧 詹姆斯
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.93,0:52:22.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,你现在能看见我们两个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.00,0:52:24.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.71,0:52:28.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,应该拒绝这种极度无聊的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.22,0:52:33.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,-好了 出发吧 我们只剩3公里了 -没错
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.38,0:52:36.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的妈呀
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.21,0:52:37.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,太臭了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.87,0:52:41.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,-这是什么 -我很不忍心 但还是要送给你这个小礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.33,0:52:45.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,真的吗 好兄弟 -没错 是我车载生态的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.66,0:52:46.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.93,0:52:49.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,-是一只死掉的蝙蝠 -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.81,0:52:52.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,-蝙蝠靠超声波飞行? -没错
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.40,0:52:55.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,那我就可以把它当倒车雷达了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.39,0:52:58.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,可我觉得它死了之后就没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.51,0:53:03.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,于是我们又上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.95,0:53:09.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的蝙蝠牌倒车雷达很好使
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.81,0:53:14.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,踏上这史诗路程的最后3公里
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.82,0:53:16.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢 见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.95,0:53:20.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,环保主义会产生一些问题
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.56,0:53:22.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们面前的就是其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.89,0:53:32.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我是不是在门附近 -噢天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.59,0:53:40.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯决定要用一卷毛线来固定住车身
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.43,0:53:42.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,效果还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.53,0:53:44.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,滚下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.71,0:53:50.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,他肯定傻眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.75,0:53:54.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们为什么要做成一个球形呢 太愚蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.66,0:53:59.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,但最终他还是固定好了 我们继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.91,0:54:04.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯 你的车现在有多重
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.26,0:54:06.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,车重现在减轻了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.29,0:54:07.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,我觉得降到3吨了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.16,0:54:10.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以你还是需要B本才能开?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.77,0:54:13.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是交管局并不一定认得这是车
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.88,0:54:18.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,要知道 我还有个更大的麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.78,0:54:21.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的车开始变得越来越臭了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.31,0:54:25.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,其中一个录音机
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.15,0:54:26.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,正在和我的麦克风胡搞
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.90,0:54:28.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,这太恶心了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.73,0:54:33.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,终于 我们的目的地已经近在眼前了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.95,0:54:39.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,经过历尽艰辛的3天
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.30,0:54:42.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,超过18公里的旅程 我们终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.95,0:54:44.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,就是这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.02,0:54:49.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,可持续发展汽车运动挑战赛开幕仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.45,0:54:52.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,就在这条天然形成的赛道上面
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.64,0:54:56.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.72,0:54:59.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,-有短信 -什么
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.38,0:55:00.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,韦尔曼先生给我发了条短信
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.91,0:55:02.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,告诉我接下来要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.78,0:55:07.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,在一小时内完成圈数最多的人将会获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.20,0:55:08.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 詹姆斯 肯定不会是你
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.92,0:55:11.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你怎么知道 -我敢肯定不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.92,0:55:14.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢 等一下 你们还要和3辆
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.67,0:55:17.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,老式钢铁车一起比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.91,0:55:20.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,-等一下 是那几辆吧 -哪儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.28,0:55:23.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,-噢 它们来了 -好古老的车
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.87,0:55:26.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 一点也不古老 它们的样子太可笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.33,0:55:28.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,那就是自然进步的产物 很讽刺
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.11,0:55:30.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我突然觉得它们的样子蠢爆了 -没错
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.22,0:55:36.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,这些老古董由3位当地的小混混驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.93,0:55:39.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,好的 就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.73,0:55:44.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,肉车 树车和粪车都已经准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.77,0:55:52.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢 很好 起步不错
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.53,0:55:54.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,没错 就是要挡住你们
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.82,0:55:58.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢 他们开始了 我看不见旗子
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.20,0:56:02.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,我能看见一些干草堆 就沿着它们开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.51,0:56:05.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,接下来往哪边走
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.22,0:56:09.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,尽管我和理查德的起步很好
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.69,0:56:13.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,但很快我们就被钢铁车超越了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.12,0:56:15.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,高尔夫超过我了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.31,0:56:19.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢不 不
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.45,0:56:22.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,我被蒙迪欧超了 天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.71,0:56:26.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢 我鼻子里的棉条掉了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.47,0:56:29.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,理查德和我现在急需另一位同事的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.22,0:56:31.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,只可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.64,0:56:36.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,看我的走线 噢我完全迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.42,0:56:39.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,问题在于 赛道看上去和我的车头一样
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.11,0:56:42.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是谁想出来的馊主意
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.33,0:56:47.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的棉条全掉了 救命
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.38,0:56:51.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,我可能要进一次站 再塞两个棉条
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.71,0:56:53.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,我该往哪儿开
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.84,0:56:57.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,又见面了 詹姆斯
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.26,0:56:58.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.69,0:56:59.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,不能再浪费时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.80,0:57:05.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,我换上了两个
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.51,0:57:07.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,超强吸水的大号棉条
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.32,0:57:10.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,希望能多坚持一会
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.31,0:57:17.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为这是一场耐力赛
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.15,0:57:20.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以到目前为止我们都在尽量保护车子
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.11,0:57:25.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们现在需要可靠性 仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.31,0:57:26.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.98,0:57:30.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,但随着几辆古董车的一次次挑衅
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.60,0:57:32.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们也要拿出真本事了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.53,0:57:36.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在是肉车对阵...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.89,0:57:40.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,那辆1.6升的高尔夫
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.91,0:57:42.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.55,0:57:44.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,太棒了 我超过他了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.58,0:57:48.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,看我篱笆漂移
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.60,0:57:50.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.09,0:57:57.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.84,0:58:02.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,我觉得我好像跑完了一整圈
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.26,0:58:08.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,在我们三个 两个人势不可挡的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.31,0:58:11.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,几辆古董车开始不择手段了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.75,0:58:16.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,怎么能这样 他们开始用暴力了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.32,0:58:21.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢 噢不
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.59,0:58:23.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的棉条又掉了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.89,0:58:26.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,谁撞我
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.04,0:58:28.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,你以为我长得像一棵树
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.70,0:58:30.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以就好欺负是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.46,0:58:33.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,你这样是不对的 兄弟 尝尝这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.74,0:58:42.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,我在用血肉之躯对抗钢铁
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.40,0:58:46.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,尽管我们都在尽力坚持
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.47,0:58:50.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,但我们的车都开始受到不同程度的损伤
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.64,0:58:56.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的车顶掉了一块
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.38,0:59:00.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,我闻到了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.06,0:59:03.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是什么味
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.42,0:59:06.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,是我排气管里出来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.02,0:59:11.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,当哈蒙德因为车身被排气管点燃而分心之时
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.51,0:59:13.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,重任落在了我的牛车上
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.71,0:59:21.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,传统与未来在此契合
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.20,0:59:23.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们现在并驾齐驱
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.73,0:59:27.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.46,0:59:29.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢不
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.89,0:59:31.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.30,0:59:32.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,见鬼 看起来
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.59,0:59:34.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,杰瑞米遇上麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.04,0:59:38.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,该怎么把牛皮剥下来
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.44,0:59:42.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,在终于解救了过热的引擎 并且发现
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.46,0:59:46.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,它已经变成了一条蛆虫的生产线
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.26,0:59:49.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,我决定走到一边去吐一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.36,0:59:57.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,呃 可持续发展汽车运动挑战赛的最新消息
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.91,0:59:59.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,来自于一条所谓的可持续发展赛道
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.04,1:00:03.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,杰瑞米 克拉克森因为蛆虫问题退赛了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.38,1:00:08.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,因此全部的希望都寄托在了理查德 哈蒙德
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.64,1:00:10.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,和他燃烧的方舟上
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.84,1:00:14.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,哈哈 你走线太宽了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.09,1:00:16.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,可是好景不长
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.80,1:00:18.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢 天呐
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.60,1:00:20.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢不
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.97,1:00:24.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦不 关于这场
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.39,1:00:27.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,可持续汽车挑战赛更多的新闻有
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.88,1:00:30.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,我觉得理查德哈蒙德的车着火了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.58,1:00:32.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,花园中心亮起了火光
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.58,1:00:36.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢 上帝啊 不 不要这样
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.35,1:00:40.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,这样只会越烧越旺
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.38,1:00:44.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,随着哈蒙德的车着了火
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.62,1:00:50.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的车出了虫子 詹姆斯的车还在瓦解
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.20,1:00:51.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,嗷 嗷
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.71,1:00:55.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们得出了结论 环保主义根本行不通
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.84,1:00:59.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,接下来 把画面
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.53,1:01:01.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,接下来 把画面切回帐篷里
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.13,1:01:05.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,我靠
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.64,1:01:14.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,-根本行不通 -没错 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.46,1:01:18.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,就是这样 我们调查过了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.75,1:01:20.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们彻彻底底的调查过之后
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.33,1:01:23.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,恐怕我们没救了 我们都会死
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.83,1:01:27.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,随着这个令人十分沮丧的消息 这期节目就结束了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.18,1:01:28.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,下周见 拜拜
